{
    "strings":  {
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_KNIFE_DESC":  "As Nemesis Mercenary, defeat a different vestige.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_STICKYOVERLOADER_DESC":  "As MUL-T, collect 20 green items in a single run.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PUNCH_NAME":  "fujin",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_CLONE_DESC":  "As Nemesis Mercenary, purchase a Duplicator Drone.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_PICKUP":  "All attacks strike an additional time. \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eLowered attack speed and increased skill cooldowns\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_FIRINGSQUAD_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eShocking\u003c/style\u003e. Summon a firing squad of ion guns, rapidly firing ion bullets for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e350% damage\u003c/style\u003e per bullet but losing \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e-60% movement speed\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eHold to extend duration. Cooldown scales with usage length.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_UTILITY_DODGE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eRoll\u003c/style\u003e a short distance, temporarily gaining \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e200 armor\u003c/style\u003e. Hold up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e2\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_PORTAL_VOIDSHOP_APPEAR":  "\u003cstyle=cEvent\u003eA mysterious portal appears somewhere..\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_UNIVERSALCHARGER_NAME":  "Universal Charger",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Nemesis Mercenary, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_DESC":  "A \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003echoice\u003c/style\u003e between three \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003epowerful items\u003c/style\u003e appears at the \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estart of each stage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_LORE":  "Ah, Youngling! You have returned once more, with what seems to be a full bag, too! Full of scavengings, yes?\n\nHmm. The pack is heavy, but it is nearly empty. You... You are not hiding things from me, Youngling?\n\n...You found something very heavy. I see. Forgive me for my suspicions. Show me this thing you have found.\n\nAh! You are correct, Youngling. This thing is small, but difficult to hold. It splinters and fragments, and each piece is just as heavy as the whole. What a remarkable thing, this is!\n\nI will put it with the other wonderful things you have found. A thing like this could be dangerous if it fell into the wrong hands. As for you, Youngling... Hmm, I believe some repairs for your bag are in order. Come with me.",
                    "SS2_ENGINEER_LASERFOCUS_NAME":  "Laser Focus",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COFFEEBAG_PICKUP":  "Drop coffee beans that boost attack and movement speed.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_RULE_NAME":  "Damage Received by Players",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_COGNATION_DESC":  "Complete the Trial of Cognation",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_SECONDARY_SHIELD_DESC":  "Raise your shield, gaining \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e400 armor\u003c/style\u003e. Use before an incoming strike to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eparry\u003c/style\u003e it and \u003ccolor=#fa78f3\u003eEmpower\u003c/color\u003e your next skill.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GALVANICCORE_PICKUP":  "Stunned enemies apply a debuff to nearby enemies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_INSECTICIDE_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e chance to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003epoison\u003c/style\u003e an enemy for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e base damage.",
                    "SS2_DROIDDRONE_SKILL_DESCRIPTION":  "",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Commando is a wildcard on the battlefield, capable of turning any situation to his favor.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Single Tap can be used to deal with foes at any distance. Combine it with Blade of Cessation up close to shred foes.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Gouge is a powerful debuff that can critical hit and activate item effects, on top of its heavy damage.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Proper balance of melee and ranged combat is key, and Tactical Roll grants high armor to help enter and exit battles.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Disrupt enemies with Submission, whether it be to aid in an escape or get the jump on an unsuspecting target.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BORG_DESC":  "",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_STAGGER":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eStagger\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eInterrupts enemies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SANTAHAT_PICKUP":  "Gotcha!",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GREENCHOCOLATE_DESC":  "When damaged for at least \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e of your max HP, the excess damage is reduced by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e, and also gain a buff that grants \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e+{4}%\u003c/style\u003e base damage and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e+{5}%\u003c/style\u003e critical chance for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}s\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{3}s per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. ",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MALICE_NAME":  "Malice",
                    "SS2_MULE_NET_NAME":  "Immobilize",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_100_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+100% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_LORE":  "This planet sucks man.. *takes hit from cigar*",
                    "SS2_SKILL_DISABLED_DESCRIPTION":  "This skill has been disabled.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_CHIRRWITHER2":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eWither\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eHealth decays over time, and a portion of damage taken is \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003epermanent\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_EXECUTION_DESC":  "Leap into the air, then slam an ion axe for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1450% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Hitting an isolated target deals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edouble damage\u003c/style\u003e and restores 3 \u003ccolor=#29e5f2\u003eIon Charges\u003c/color\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_MAGNET_NAME":  "Simple Magnet",
                    "SS2_ACIDBUG_BODY_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_50_DECREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "-50% Damage Received",
                    "SS2_SKIN_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_NEMESIS":  "Honorable",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_NAME":  "Ethereal Sapling",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GREENCHOCOLATE_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eAudio transcription complete from signal echoes. Assigning generic tokens.\u003c/style\u003e\n\n[Hissing, loud clank]\n\nMAN 1: Uh... Hey, weird question?\n\nMAN 2: [Audible sigh] What?\n\nMAN 1: Do you know of any weird, exotic chocolates that are bright green in color?\n\nMAN 2: What? What on Earth are you on about?\n\nMAN 1: I found some green chocolate in this security chest, and I\u0027m asking if that\u0027s normal or not.\n\nMAN 2: Uh, no, it\u0027s not. I don\u0027t think so, anyways. I wouldn\u0027t know.\n\n[Crinkling]\n\nMAN 1: So then what\u0027s it supposed to be? Do you think this is poisonous, too?\n\nMAN 2: Probably not. And, ugh, for the last time, the meat wasn\u0027t poisonous, you\u0027ve just got a weak stomach.\n\nMAN 1: Alright, I guess I\u0027ll keep it, for if things get desperate.\n\nMAN 2: That\u0027s probably not a great idea, but alright.\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003e End of requested transcript.\u003c/style\u003e\n",
                    "SS2_DUT_DESCRIPTION":  "Seriously this is a very rough early prototype of DU-T, Enjoy it as a novelty, but its buggy.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFECHELON_DESC":  "Gain {1} (+{1} per stack) base damage and {2} (+{2} per stack) base health for {3} seconds on use. Using an equipment ermanently increases its cooldown by {0}%",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_ROCKFRUIT_PICKUP":  "Transmute a random item.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HITLIST_LORE":  "???",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Cyborg, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_PYRO_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Pyro, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SUBTITLE":  "Down with the Ship",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_LORE":  "Ah, welcome back! Youngling, what have you found?\n\nHmmm. More scavengings from the blasted heath? Very well. You may keep those things, if you wish. Have you found anything else?\n\nAh, you have? Let me see it then, youngling.\n\nOh! This shape that you\u0027ve found! It is stalwart, but not loyal. Powerful, but yet also frail at the same time. It is a peculiar shape, to say the least of it. Where did you find this, youngling?\n\n...You found it on the planet? Hmm. Worrisome. This was not created by those sandfolk. Too complex, too powerful. Nor by those Lemurians. Tell me, youngling, you did not steal this, did you?\n\n...You did not. I see. Very well. I would like to keep this shape. This shape is dangerous if you do not understand it.\n\nOh, my youngling, do not look so saddened. This shape is remarkable, and I laud your work regardless of this. I simply want to keep it safe. Here, perhaps a reward is in order. Come with me.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GUARDINGAMULET_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_HAIDARA_NAME":  "raijin",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SNAKEEYES_NAME":  "SnakeEyes",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_BACKTHRUSTER_PICKUP":  "Moving in a straight line rapidly builds up speed.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_DEFAULT_NAME_TOKEN":  "Default Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SPECIAL_NAME":  "Splatter",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_SWINGAXE_NAME":  "Executioner: Slayer",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONBLAST_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire a blast of raw ion energy for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Can be \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003echarged\u003c/style\u003e, using multiple charges at once. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eRestocks charges for every enemy you kill, depending on strength\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_SECONDARY_SHIELD_DESC2":  "Raise your shield, gaining \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e400 armor\u003c/style\u003e and replacing your jump with a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eroll\u003c/style\u003e. Use before an incoming strike to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eparry\u003c/style\u003e it and \u003ccolor=#fa78f3\u003eEmpower\u003c/color\u003e your next skill.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PRIMARY_DESCRIPTION":  "Rapidly fire for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e90% damage\u003c/style\u003e per bullet. Can hold up to 20 bullets.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKE_NAME":  "ORDER: Strike",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, an empty shell of armor drenched in blood.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_HEADBUTT_NAME":  "Headbutt",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONBLAST_NAME":  "Ion Blast",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_TOOLBOT_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "MUL-T: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMERC_NAME":  "Vengeful Deserter",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_PISTOL_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire your pistol for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e180% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BORG_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Cyborg, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_DESCRIPTION":  "The future of law enforcement. Warden is a ",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_DESC":  "Slay an Empyrean elite.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLOODTESTER_PICKUP":  "Periodically heal based on gold.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_COMPOSITEINJECTOR_NAME":  "Too Much Stuff!",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_LORE":  "WIP LORE",
                    "SS2_EVENT_OVERLOADINGELITE_START":  "Overloading energies materialize...",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_WEATHERRADIO_NAME":  "I Am The Storm",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_DELUGE_NAME":  "Deluge",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_LORE":  "WIP LORE",
                    "SS2_UNLOCKABLE_LOG_LAMPBOSS":  "Logbook: Wayfarer",
                    "SS2_EVENT_MENDINGELITE_END":  "Soothing energies fade away...",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_UTILITY_TELEPORTER_NAME":  "Recall",
                    "SS2_PYRO_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, his heart burning with passion.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONBURST_NAME":  "Ion Burst",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SANTAHAT_DESC":  "Lookin\u0027 jolly.",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_PRIMARY_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire a revolver shot for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e220% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Can hold up to 6 bullets.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_PRIMARY_BOW_NAME":  "Heavy Bolt",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_POISONOUSGLAND_DESC":  "As Acrid, poison 500 enemies.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_CYCLONE3_NAME":  "Cyclone +3",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SKATEBOARD_NAME":  "Swift Skateboard",
                    "SS2_LAMPBOSS_BODY_NAME":  "Wayfarer",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SECONDARY_LASER_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire laser blasts at up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e3\u003c/style\u003e targets, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e3x150% damage\u003c/style\u003e and \u003ccolor=#42f5b3\u003ePriming\u003c/color\u003e enemies.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_CLOAKINGHEADBAND_PICKUP":  "Become temporarily invisible and gain a speed boost.",
                    "SS2_TRADER_QUALITY_POOR":  "\u003cb\u003ePoor\u003c/b\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RAINBOWROOT_DESC":  "Gain \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e3\u003c/style\u003e orbiting branches. After taking damage equal to or more than 25% of max health, a branch breaks, granting 25% of max health as barrier. Branches recharge after 20s.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DROIDHEAD_PICKUP":  "Spawn a temporary drone upon killing an elite enemy.",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_PRIMARY_BLADE_NAME":  "Blade of Cessation",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_STRESSPASSIVE_DESC":  "Gain \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eStress\u003c/style\u003e while in danger. When Stress reaches maximum, temporarily become \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eOverstressed\u003c/style\u003e, reducing \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e, \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003earmor\u003c/style\u003e, and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edamage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GUARDINGAMULET_PICKUP":  "Reduce damage taken from behind",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CROCO_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Acrid, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or Harder.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BORG_MASTERY_DESC":  "As Cyborg, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eRecharging.\u003c/style\u003e Fire a barrage of ionized bullets, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e each. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eUp to 5 charges are fired at a time\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_GREATERWARBANNER_NAME":  "Greater Warbanner",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_PICKUP":  "All attacks burn enemies. \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eAll damage freezes you.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_UTILITY_DODGE_NAME":  "Tactical Roll",
                    "SS2_LAMP_BODY_LORE":  "Oh, dear. Look at you, poor thing.\n\nYou\u0027re freezing.\n\nHere, now. You\u0027ve been through so much already.\n\n...\n\nThere we go. Your flame has reignited. That will keep you warm, for now.\n\nCome with me. I\u0027ll introduce you to the others.\n\nOh? Of course there are others. It\u0027d be cruel to be the only one of your kind, wouldn\u0027t it?\n\nCome, now! Don\u0027t tarry. They\u0027ll share their warmth with you. Just follow me.\n\nYou\u0027ll be safe here.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_SPECIAL_BANNER_NAME":  "Rally",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NKOTASHERITAGE_DESC":  "Carry 25 unique items in a single run.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COFFEEBAG_LORE":  "Order: Coffee\nTracking Number: 917****\nEstimated Delivery: 12/06/2056\nShipping Method: Standard\nShipping Address: 4410 New Lane, Kentucky, Earth\nShipping Details:\n\nHi, Mom!\n\nI\u0027ve been out traveling, just as you did in your youth... I remember all the stories you used to tell me from when you were my age. Going to places like Jamaicia, Romania, pretty much everywhere on Earth! I hope I can visit home soon so I can tell you about all the places I\u0027ve been.\n\nI remember there was this great coffee you used to get us back home... was it \"Neik Dark Roast\"? Anyway, there\u0027s this great place out on Titan that grows their own coffee, and it\u0027s some of the best! Reminds me of being home with you.\n\nI hope I can see you soon. I miss you, and I miss the cats. Rose says hi, and I can\u0027t wait to tell you about everything!\n\nLove, Hanan\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NANOBOTS_PICKUP":  "Gain armor. Duplicates itself when scrapped.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STICKYOVERLOADER_NAME":  "Sticky Overloader",
                    "SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_ELECTRO":  "Electrocutioner",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONBOSSKILL_PICKUP":  "Bosses drop items.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_ATTACKVECTOR":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eAttack Vector\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eInterrupts enemies.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_X4_DESC":  "As Huntress, kill 7 unique bosses in one run.",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_SKYMEADOW":  "Turn away from the moon.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_SUPERTYPHOON_DESC":  "",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SECONDARY_CONCUSSION_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eGouging.\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile.\u003c/style\u003e Hold to charge a piercing sword beam for up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_MASTERY_NAME":  "Nemesis Commmando: Mastery",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he vanished, escaping the inevitable.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_CHIRRBUFF":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eAccelerate\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eIncreases \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eattack speed\u003c/style\u003e.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_LAMPBOSS_BODY_LORE":  "LITTLE ONES, GATHER HERE TO ME. I MUST WARN YOU OF SOMETHING.\n\n...\n\nTHE TRAVELER HAS RETURNED TO THIS REALM.\n\nLONG AGO, I SUBDUED HIM, BANISHED HIM FROM OUR GARDEN. BUT NOW, HE THREATENS OUR HOME ONCE AGAIN.\n\nIF YOU SEE HIM, DO NOT LISTEN TO HIM. HE WILL TRY TO SWAY YOU TO HIS SIDE, WITH PROMISES OF WARMTH AND SAFETY AND STRENGTH.\n\nIT IS A TRAP.\n\nONCE HE HAS YOUR TRUST, YOU WILL BE A SLAVE TO HIS LIGHT. YOU WILL BEAR YOUR OWN CHAINS, JUST AS HE BEARS HIS OWN.\n\n...\n\nBUT - DO NOT WORRY. I WILL PROTECT THE GARDEN. IF HE HAS THE AUDACITY TO RETURN TO ME, THAT IS.\n\nAS FOR YOU, LITTLE ONES, I HAVE A GIFT FOR EACH AND EVERY ONE OF YOU. COME CLOSER.\n\nCLOSER NOW!\n\nNOW, WATCH - WATCH HERE. WATCH MY HAND.\n\nYOU ALL WILL HELP ME TEND TO THE GARDEN.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_NAME":  "Overkill",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SKIN_DEFAULT":  "Default",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_EXECUTING":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eExecuting\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDeals doubled damage if no more than 1 enemy is hit.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SPECIAL_SCEPBOSS_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eGouging.\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eCharge up\u003c/style\u003e, then \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003edash forward\u003c/style\u003e and unleash a devastating barrage of up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0} slashes\u003c/style\u003e that deal up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}% damage each\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eThe number of slashes increases with attack speed\u003c/style\u003e. \n\u003ccolor=#d299ff\u003eSCEPTER: At full charge, briefly vanish, then unleash all of your strikes at once.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_90_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players deal 10% damage.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_HUNTRESS_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Huntress: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_EMPYREAN":  "Empyrean{0} {1}",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_GREATERWARBANNER_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eRecording from the Terran Museum of Tactics and Warfare.\u003c/style\u003e\n\nSome say that one of the most important resources on the battlefield is morale. The functionality of a unit is exponentially increased depending on the mood of the troops within it. This can be raised or lowered through various means. For example, the quality of their lodging or food, news they\u0027ve heard from their home, or even spending time recreationally.\n\nHowever, one tried and true method of raising the morale of a unit is the usage of symbolism. Many armies would wear colors and designs symbolizing their beliefs and their strength. Many units would carry flags in order to keep their morale high in combat.\n\nThe usage of this method has also seen variations. While a flag bearer for a unit will increase morale, it has been observed that flags unique to higher ranking military will further increase the unit\u0027s morale. Should a Colonel or General\u0027s flag appear on the battlefield, the troops will be encouraged by the power they display, and in turn increase their own fighting prowess.\n",
                    "SS2_INTERACTABLE_SANTAHAT_CONTEXT":  "GRAB IT! GRAB IT!",
                    "SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_DESC":  "Grants \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e Legendary Chest \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eon each stage\u003c/style\u003e, \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003ebut you cannot leave without claiming your birthright\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERFIRE_NAME":  "Royal Flame(?)",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FIELDACCELERATOR_NAME":  "Field Accelerator",
                    "SS2_BORG_PRIMARY_GUN_NAME":  "Unmaker",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_GOUGE":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eGouge\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eApplies 100% damage over time, capable of critical hits.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_HOTTESTSAUCE_NAME":  "Hot Mix",
                    "KEYWORD_SS2_TELEFRAG":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eTelefragging\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDeals heavy damage to enemies when teleporting inside of them.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_TRADER_QUALITY_MODERATE":  "\u003cb\u003eFine\u003c/b\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_LORE":  "“Hey!“\n\n\nA figure slowly hobbled out from the sandy Martian dunes, tuning into Fort Laughn\u0027s external communications. “Hey, mind letting me in? Dust out here is killing me.“\n\n\n \nOne of the stationed guards on the outer fence quipped back from a booth. “...You got credentials, sir?“\n\n\n\n“Come on, you don\u0027t recognize me? Let me guess- new recruit? Something like that?“ The figure continued walking nonchalantly toward the fence as a second guard piped up. “Hold on. Is that Vantre?“ The guest laughed, still wandering every-which-way as he came closer to the fence. “Guilty as charged. Thought I\u0027d stop by while I\u0027m in the area. Say hey to some old comrades, maybe.“\n\n\n\nThe guards paused, then, on a separate line, rang up their CO. “Commanding Officer Byren, Vantre\u0027s at the outer fence. He appears non-threatening, which is an immediate red flag. What\u0027re your orders?“\n\n\n\nByren\u0027s scratchy, exasperated voice chirped back through the receiver. “Ugh, damnitâ€¦ Page the suppression crew. Make sure he\u0027s not trying anything, alright? Keep him busy until you\u0027ve got more people out there.“ The guard relayed the order- “Get a crew out here. I\u0027ll make sure Vantre doesn\u0027t try anything stupid.“ The recruit replied with a question: “Sure, but, uhhâ€¦ Where\u0027d he go?“\n\n\n\nSure enough, Vantre had vanished while the two were distracted, leaving nothing but sparks in the air where he once stood. It took the entirety of the fort\u0027s stationed force about ten minutes to figure out what was going on- and they found out at about the same time they found their commanding officer dead in his quarters, the back of his head blasted to smithereens.\n",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_LORE":  "Death is inevitable. It comes for us all. Some may try to evade it, or run from it. But death arrives all the same. Death, however, is simply the cost of war. And death in glorious combat is one of the best deaths a man could ask for.\n\nBut, as always, some would seek to run from death. We call them by many names. Deserters, cowards, turncoats. Each and every one of them, traitors to the cause. These traitors must be punished for their crime. And that punishment: in an ironic twist, is the very thing they tried to avoid.\n\nDeath will come for them. Not as a robed spectre with a scythe. Not in a trench coat, holding a revolver. Not as a sickness, nor the wear of time. No. For them, death will come bearing lustrous battlegarb, with service pistol loaded, and ion manipulators fully charged.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_UTILITY_SLIDE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eStunning.\u003c/style\u003e Hold to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eslide\u003c/style\u003e while preparing a targeted dash that deals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e600% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_MULE_UPHEAVAL_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Punch the ground in front of you, raising a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eboulder\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e450% damage\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eBoulders can be punched to be rolled.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PRIMARY_NAME":  "Standard Issue",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_50_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players take 150% damage.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_DESC":  "Defeat an enemy by dealing 1000% of its max health in damage.",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_FROZENWALL":  "The loneliest tree.",
