                    "SS2_PYRO_SECONDARY_ALT_DESC":  "\u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e30% heat\u003c/color\u003e. Fire a burst of flames, \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003eigniting\u003c/color\u003e enemies for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ereflecting projectiles\u003c/style\u003e. Extra stocks \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003ereduce heat consumption by 15%\u003c/color\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_KEYWORD_OVERSTRESS":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eOverstress\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eBecome subjected to the effects of maximum Stress, as well as -30% movement speed, -20 armor, and -50% damage until the Stress meter counts down to 0.",
