                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SECONDARY_SHOOT_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile.\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eRending.\u003c/style\u003e Fire your gun for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
