                    "SS2_KNIGHT_SHIELD_BASH_NAME":  "Bash",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_75_DECREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "-75% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_LORE":  "why are there knights in space",
                    "SS2_PYRO_NAME":  "Pyro",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_PRIMARY_SWORD_DESC":  "Swing your sword for X% damage with the 3rd hit stabbing forward for X% damage",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SKATEBOARD_PICKUP":  "Sprint in any direction. Using skills makes you move faster.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_X4_DESC":  "Reduces secondary skill cooldown by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. Using your secondary skill \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eincreases base health regen\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e+{1} hp/s\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2} hp/s per stack)\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{3}\u003c/style\u003e seconds.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_PYRO_NAME":  "",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SNAKEEYES_DESC":  "Using a Shrine increases your \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003ecritical chance permanently\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e2%\u003cstyle=cStack\u003e (+1% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eCritical chance\u003c/style\u003e over \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e100%\u003c/style\u003e grants a chance to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ereduce your cooldowns\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e1\u003c/style\u003e second.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_COMMANDO_NEMESISSKIN_DESC":  "As Commando, defeat Commando\u0027s Vestige.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_DEFAULT":  "Default",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_SINGLETAP_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, defeat Commando\u0027s vestige.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_DESC":  "Slice forward for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e200% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Every third hit stabs forward for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e. While blocking, bash enemies for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_ALT_DESCRIPTION":  "you know what it does",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_NAME":  "\u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eMoxie\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DIARY_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eSecurity footage transmission complete of Hallway Section 14-B.\n\nPrinting...\n\n\u003c/style\u003e\"So this book\u0027s the only thing in the storage container?\"\n\"Pretty much. Other than some old furniture, this is it.\"\n\"So what\u0027s this book\u0027s deal? If this is all we\u0027re getting, it better be good.\"\n\"It\u0027s a diary, I think. First written in by one Alan Howizer, about 26 years ago. Seemed like a pretty smart guy, said he worked at a chemical testing plant back on Earth.\"\n\"That\u0027s it? This is just some old guy\u0027s diary?\"\n\"Hold on, there\u0027s more to it. While I was flipping through, about a hundred pages in, the handwriting changed, and sure enough, it was found by a different person on a park bench, apparently. Same thing again, about thirty pages later. And again, after about another seventy. And it keeps on going. There\u0027s a couple dozen different people who wrote in this diary, writing down their fond memories, odd mysteries, riddles, their answers to those riddles, all sorts of things.\"\n\"Huh. This thing must be a real treasure trove of knowledge then, yeah? Any clue as to who last owned it?\"\n\"Uh, yeah, actually. Someone named Chel was the last one to write in the book, and it looks like they left an address inside the back cover. Why, what are you thinking?\"\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eEnd of notable section.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_50_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+50% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLOODTESTER_NAME":  "Broken Blood Tester",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CRYPTICSOURCE_DESC":  "As Mercenary, complete 3 Ethereal teleporters in one run.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, battered to the core of hope.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_PASSIVE_DESC":  "A buff ward surronds you that grants allies in its radius IDK YET IT ISNT WORKING",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HITLIST_PICKUP":  "Attack marked enemies to gain gold, and a permanent damage boost on kill.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_NAME":  "Relic of Termination",
                    "SS2_EVENT_ASHSTORM_START":  "\u003csprite name=\"CloudRight\"\u003e\t An ash storm is approaching...",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_PICKUP":  "\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eWhat am I fighting for?\u003c/link\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SPECIAL_BOSS_NAME":  "Decisive Strike",
