                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_75_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+75% Damage Received",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_ELECTRO_DESC":  "As Executioner, defeat an Overloading Worm using Execution.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_NAME":  "Crowd Dispersion",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_COGNATION_DESC":  "Enemies leave behind temporary duplicates on death.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_ROCKFRUIT_NAME":  "Rock Fruit",
                    "SS2_BORG_SUBTITLE":  "Man Made Monstrosity",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLASTKNUCKLES_DESC":  "Hits from your \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eskills\u003c/style\u003e within \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}m\u003c/style\u003e also \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eblast\u003c/style\u003e enemies in a cone for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e base damage. You can hold up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e5\u003c/style\u003e charges and reload a charge every \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e5\u003c/style\u003e seconds.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_DESC":  "WIP DESC",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_NAME":  "Stirring Soul",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_COGNATION_NAME":  "Artifact of Cognation",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_CYCLONE1_NAME":  "Cyclone +1",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, newfound sense of humanity within.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTNINGONKILL_DESC":  "On killing an enemy, create an \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eelectric discharge\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% base damage\u003c/style\u003e on up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e targets within \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{3}m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{4}m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e meters.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKETRIPLE_NAME":  "ORDER: Strike 3x",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_SUPEREARTH":  "Tectonic {0}",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_ETHEREAL":  "Ethereal {0}",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_TASER_DESC":  "Fire arcs of lightning forward for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e80% damage\u003c/style\u003e that can \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003echain\u003c/style\u003e between enemies up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e4 additional times\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ERRATICGADGET_PICKUP":  "Lightning strikes twice.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Executioner takes away the lives of those who are lost in a coup de grace for what he envisions as the greater welfare.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Death doesn\u0027t fear itself.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NEEDLES_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e+{0}% chance\u003c/style\u003e on hit to guarantee \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003ecritical strikes\u003c/style\u003e on an enemy for the next \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e hits.",
                    "SS2_VOIDROCK_CONTEXT":  "Get Mysterious Cuff",
                    "SS2_ITEM_CHUNGUS_PICKUP":  "Heal all nearby allies after standing still for 1 second. \u003cstyle=cIsVoid\u003eCorrupts all Dormant Fungi\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXPURPLE_NAME":  "Malignant Resolve",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_PRIMARY_SHOTGUN_NAME":  "Splatter",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BABYTOYS_DESC":  "Lose up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0} \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e levels\u003c/style\u003e while \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eretaining all stats\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GREENCHOCOLATE_PICKUP":  "Reduce damage taken and gain a huge damage and critical chance bonus upon taking heavy damage.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_DESCRIPTION":  "Chirr is a mystical creature who holds a pure connection with the planet and its inhabitants.\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Chirr\u0027s ability to sprint while hovering makes her incredibly agile in the air. Try to maximize airtime to stay safe and dodge attacks.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Soothing Venom both heals allies and damages enemies in a radius. Try to position your friend- or yourself- near groups of enemies to maximize the effect.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Abduct is an incredibly versatile skill that can be used to buff your allies, fly to safety, group targets together, or lock down a tough enemy.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Symbiotic Link allows you to befriend an enemy under 50% health, giving it a copy of your inventory. Your friend constantly loses health over time, so it is vital to support them with your other abilities.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_DEVIATION_NAME":  "Artifact of Deviation",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_TASER_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire arcs of lightning forward for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Captain issues orders to control the battlefield and fight safely from behind his Adaptive Microbots.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Keep your cool. Using Orders too quickly will build Stress, leaving you vulnerable.",
                    "SS2_DROIDDRONE_NAME":  "Security Drone",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COMPOSITEINJECTOR_PICKUP":  "Combine equipment items.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_URANIUMHORSESHOE_LORE":  "funny",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MOLTENCOIN_NAME":  "Molten Coin",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_PISTOL_NAME":  "Service Pistol",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FIELDACCELERATOR_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003e//--AUTO-TRANSCRIPTION FROM ROOM 1455A OF UES [Safe Travels]--//\u003c/style\u003e\n\n\"Do you have the device?\"\n\n\"Yes, it\u0027s right here.\"\n\n\"It works, right?\"\n\n\"Mmmhmm. Flawlessly.\"\n\n\"Excellent. Remember, no one can know about this.\"\n\n\"Yes, yes, I know. Those... altars, on [REDACTED] have fantastic potential. Once we\u0027ve analyzed them, replicating them should be a cinch. It\u0027ll be a massive scientific breakthrough.\"\n\n\"Good. Just keep low, get your analysis, and get out before anyone gets suspicious.\"\n\n\"Will do. Again, thank you so much for your help.\"\n\n\"It\u0027s nothing. As long as you\u0027re paying me.\"\n\n\"Eh-heh, about that...\"",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_HEADBUTT_DESCRIPTION":  "As Chirr, throw 20 beetles off the edge of the map.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BANEFLASK_DESC":  "Spread debuffs on kill or something also has a debuff owie that hurts",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_BACKTHRUSTER_NAME":  "Back Thruster",
                    "SS2_RULEBOOK_DESC":  "Customize basic rules of your run to better suit your taste.",
                    "SS2_VOIDROCK_NAME":  "Mysterious Cuff",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_UTILITY_TAUNT_NAME":  "Show Me A Good Time!",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_RULE_NAME":  "Damage Dealt by Players",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_NEMCAPEQUIP_NAME":  "Morleys",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_CLOAKINGHEADBAND_LORE":  "Order: Cloaking Headband\nTracking Number: 554*****\nEstimated Delivery: 08/01/2056\nShipping Method: Standard\nShipping Address: 202 W. Calbury Ln, Adora, Mercury\nShipping Details:\n\nI was finally able to get ahold of a personal cloaking device for you. Sneaking around in places you shouldn\u0027t be should be a cinch with this puppy.\n\nNow, there\u0027s a couple a\u0027 things you should understand about this thing. First, the cloaking only lasts a short time since the device is so small, so keep yourself hidden while it cools down again. Secondly, you need to hit the button on the headband to activate it. Not exactly a very clandestine action, I know, but it\u0027s what I could find for you.\n\nLast, if the box you get seems like it\u0027s completely empty, just feel around in the bottom until you find the button. It saves time, money, and privacy to ship it without the Volatile treatment. Tell me when this gets to you, and have fun with your new toy.\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_NAME":  "Scavenger\u0027s Fortune",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_MAID_DESC":  "As Chirr, cleanse three Lunar items in a single run.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_UTILITY_BLINK_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eBlink\u003c/style\u003e behind an enemy or \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eattack vector.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_PRIMARY_BOW_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile\u003c/style\u003e. Hold to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003echarge\u003c/style\u003e, and release to fire an arrow for up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Arrow \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003evelocity\u003c/style\u003e, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edamage\u003c/style\u003e, and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eaccuracy\u003c/style\u003e scale with charge level.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_DASH_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eDash\u003c/style\u003e forward and inspire \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003efear\u003c/style\u003e in nearby enemies.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_BODY_LORE":  "“Once, a world was formed. A mother and her two sons dwelt upon it.\n\nThe world was a reflection of its settlers. The mother would ensure her sons would learn the ways of this world, just as she shaped into something they could build upon. And so, the sons grew wise and strong, and the world flourished...“\n\n“...As the sons grew old, so did their mother. Soon came time for her to depart - but before she did, she left two gifts. One for her sons, and one for the world.\n\nFor the sons she was leaving, she gave the gift of ambition and compassion. Together, they would achieve anything they could imagine. They would make paradise. For the world she was leaving, she created life. The world\u0027s first true natives. They would be the world\u0027s caretakers, and together, its very essence...“\n\n- Galactic Fables, Volumes I and III",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DORMANTFUNGUS_PICKUP":  "Heal while sprinting.",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_LORE":  "He lays to rest by a fire, setting the weapons he carries within an arm\u0027s reach. Checking his surroundings, hoping the cave he hid in would be enough shelter. Some would say, it isn\u0027t wise to be overly cautious. He would say, \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003ethey haven\u0027t seen enough.\u003c/color\u003e\n\nThe service pistol he got when he enlisted. Well used, dirtied, and loved. It\u0027s brought him through thick and thin, no matter which mission he took on. Some would say, only a fool would trust their weapon. He would say, \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eyour weapon is all you can trust.\u003c/color\u003e\n\nThe blade of a fallen brother of war. Picked from what he could scavenge of the last of humanity he\u0027s seen. Some would say, it keeps their spirits united. He would say, \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eit\u0027s to keep their spirits from joining for as long as possible.\u003c/color\u003e\n\nThe loads of cargo that landed with him. Each item picked from a chest, keeping him alive in one way or another. Dozens of shipments to anyone but him. Some would say, they aren\u0027t his items to take. He would say, \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eif he doesn\u0027t take them, then no one will.\u003c/color\u003e\n\nThe glow of a violet light coming from deeper within the cave. Calming, warming... beckoning. Welcoming him deeper and deeper, promising safety. Some would say, what sounds too good to be true probably is. He would say, \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eFaust was a wise man.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SECONDARY_KNIFE_NAME":  "Perforator",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_GRAB_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eGrab\u003c/style\u003e a target, then quickly \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eascend\u003c/style\u003e. Release them to deal \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1500% damage\u003c/style\u003e in an area on impact. Allies gain \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e100% attack speed\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MOLTENCOIN_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e chance to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eignite\u003c/style\u003e enemies on hit for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e base damage \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e and earn \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e${2}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+${2} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eScales over time\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_WHITEFLAG_PICKUP":  "Place a white flag that disables skill usage in an area.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_HUNTERSSIGIL_NAME":  "Hunter\u0027s Strike",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_LORE":  "A spirit of determination...\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e...A spirit to be stopped.\u003c/link\u003e\nAn unwavering will to survive...\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e...A flickering will to survive.\u003c/link\u003e\n\nWilling to desecrate their identity...\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e...Willing to desecrate their memory.\u003c/link\u003e\nWilling to sacrifice their civilization...\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e...Willing to sacrifice their humanity.\u003c/link\u003e\n\nTo what lengths will they go to live?\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eTo what lengths will they go to bring themselves ruin?\u003c/link\u003e\nTo what lengths will they go to escape?\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eTo what lengths will they go to destroy?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nAll in the name of self preservation...\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e...All in the name of narcissism.\u003c/link\u003e\nAll for the sake of an uncertain hope...\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e...All for the sake of a null chance.\u003c/link\u003e\n\nWhat would happen if given an opportunity?\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eWhat would happen if given an ally?\u003c/link\u003e\nWhat would happen if their fire was stoked?\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eWhat would happen if they were given false hope?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nMaybe they should be given a chance.\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eMaybe they should be given strength.\u003c/link\u003e\nMaybe they should be given an offer.\n\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eMaybe they should be taken first.\u003c/link\u003e",
                    "SS2_EVENT_GENERICNEMESIS_END":  "The mysterious influence fades away...\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BLASTKNUCKLES_NAME":  "One Punch",
                    "SS2_SKIN_MERCENARY_VESTIGE":  "Heel",
                    "SS2_BORG_SPECIAL_TELEPORT_DESCRIPTION":  " \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eTelefragging\u003c/style\u003e. Place a teleportation beacon. Once the beacon is set, recast to teleport to it. Teleporting \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ereduces skill cooldowns by 4 seconds\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_CHEST_CONTEXT":  "Claim Birthright",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_MIDAS_NAME":  "M.I.D.A.S.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXESCEPTER_NAME":  "Crowd Execution",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_STRANGECAN_NAME":  "Another Bite",
                    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_LORE":  "WIP LORE",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKEFROST_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eFreezing\u003c/style\u003e. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eexploding\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1100% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_DESC":  "Defeat Commando\u0027s vestige.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_DIARY_NAME":  "Dear Diary...",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Chirr, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_PRIMARY_SHOTGUN_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile\u003c/style\u003e. Fire a shotgun blast for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6x80% damage\u003c/style\u003e, and again when released. Can hold up to 2 shells.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_RECOLOR1_COMMANDO_NAME":  "Commando: Scorpion",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COFFEEBAG_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e chance on hit to drop a coffee bean that grants \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}% attack speed\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{3}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eseconds\u003c/style\u003e. Maximum cap of \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e40%\u003cstyle=cStack\u003e (+40% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERNULL_DESCRIPTION":  "Devise a new plan of attack, slightly increasing \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eStress\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he vanished, with emptied munitions and an emptier heart.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_URANIUMHORSESHOE_DESC":  "As Bandit, complete stage 3 in less than 15 minutes on Typhoon difficulty.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_PICKUP":  "Grants a Legendary Chest on each stage, \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003ebut you cannot leave without claiming your birthright\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NANOBOTS_LORE":  "like the meme",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_DESCRIPTION":  "The Executioner\u0027s goal is to spill as much blood as possible in the shortest amount of time. Bullets loaded, ion manipulators charged.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e \u003c ! \u003e Use Service Pistol to score kills to charge your Ion Manipulators - or charge them manually during downtime.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Ion Burst is at its strongest when used at maximum charge. Spread its shots across a crowd to maximize its shocking effect.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Execution is a great crowd control AND single target tool. Don\u0027t forget that its damage depends on how many targets it hits!\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Use Crowd Dispersion to manipulate enemies and set them up for a well-placed Execution.",
                    "SS2_PEDESTAL_INTERACTION_HEADER":  "An Equal Trade?",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HUNTERSSIGIL_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eAudio transcription complete from portable recorder.\n\nPrinting...\n\n\u003c/style\u003e\"You think they\u0027ll take the bait?\"\n\"They\u0027re gonna have to. Not like we have any other options.\"\n\"I still think using our food like this is too risky.\"\n\"If we don\u0027t try, then we\u0027ll be dead in a week.\"\n\"Just... make sure we don\u0027t lose too much.\"\n\"Nothing more than our lives, at least.\"\n\"...\"\n\"They\u0027re here.\"\n\"Oh, good. Take one out and let\u0027s get out of here.\"\n\"Not yet...\"\n\"What? It\u0027s a waste of our food the longer you wait!\"\n\"Hold on...\"\n\"Take the shot, man, we only have so much!\"\n\"Almost...\"\n\"TAKE THE SHOT.\"\n\"Just about...\"\n\"SHOOT OR GIVE ME THE RIFLE.\"\n\"...\"\n\"GIVE IT TO ME.\"\n\"Hey, be CARE-\"\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eEnd of recording.\u003c/style\u003e\n",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SPECIAL_SCEPTER_MAGNETBALL_DESCRIPTION":  "[temp]CyborgScepterDescription",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMORSCEPTER_NAME":  "Equip a suit of ionized armor, giving \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e80 armor\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003esupercharging\u003c/style\u003e your secondary skill for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e4\u003c/style\u003e seconds. Killing enemies \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003efears\u003c/style\u003e nearby enemies for 4 seconds.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_SHIELD_BASH_DESC":  "Shield Bash in front of you for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e240% damage\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estun\u003c/style\u003e enemies hit.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_SCAN_NAME":  "Exploit",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_75_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players take 25% damage.",
                    "SS2_TRADER_CONTEXT":  "Bargain?",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NANOBOTS_DESC":  "Gain \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0} \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e armor\u003c/style\u003e. When scrapped, instead \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003edisassemble\u003c/style\u003e the scrapper into a copy of this item.",
                    "SS2_EVENT_SANDSTORM_END":  "The sand begins to settle...",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_DEVIATION_DESC":  "Choose an item for all characters before starting a teleporter event.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NANOBOTS_NAME":  "Nanobots",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_DESCRIPTION":  "The Executioner is a high-risk, high-reward survivor that\u0027s all about racking up an endless kill count.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e \u003c ! \u003e Use Service Pistol to score some kills, with each kill building up an even stronger Ion Burst.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e You can tap Ion Burst to fire a few shots, or hold it to fire them all.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Execution is a great crowd control AND single target tool. Don\u0027t forget that its damage depends on how many targets it hits!\n\n\u003c ! \u003e If you find yourself getting swarmed, Crowd Dispersion can get enemies off your back fast.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_CAPTAIN_GRANDMASTERY":  "Prestige",
                    "SS2_PYRO_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he vanished, flames finally snuffed out.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_ELECTRO_NAME":  "Executioner: Kuwabara, Kuwabara",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONCHARGE_DESC":  "Rapidly discharge \u003ccolor=#29e5f2\u003eIon Charges\u003c/color\u003e as ion bullets for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e350% damage\u003c/style\u003e. \u003ccolor=#29e5f2\u003eIon Charges\u003c/color\u003e are restored on kill.",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SPECIAL_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire a shotgun burst for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6x100% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Kills \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ereset all your cooldowns.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_OVERCLOCKING2":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eOverclocking\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/style=cSub\u003eHold the button to charge the skill further, but also extend the skill\u0027s cooldown length.\u003c/sub\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SECONDARY_SLASH_NAME":  "Cutthroat",
                    "SS2_PYRO_UTILITY_NAME":  "Ignition Check",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_MASTERY_NAME":  "Executioner: Mastery",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_SPECIAL_ALT_NAME":  "spooky mode",
                    "SS2_KNGIHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_UPRGADE_TOOLTIP":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003e\u003ccolor=#fa78f3\u003eEmpowered\u003c/color\u003e\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDash forward, and strike for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e3x400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_DRONE_CLONE_INTERACTABLE_CONTEXT":  "Repair Duplicator Drone",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Cyborg: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERICE_NAME":  "Her Cosmic Brilliance",
                    "SS2_MULE_CHARGE_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eCalibrating\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eHold to charge up\u003c/style\u003e, and release to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003efling forward\u003c/style\u003e whilst spinning for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e(medium-high damage TBD)% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_MIDAS_DESC":  "Sacrifice \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e of your \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003ecurrent health\u003c/style\u003e, gaining either the amount of \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003ehealth lost\u003c/style\u003e or \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ethe price of a standard chest\u003c/style\u003e as \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003egold\u003c/style\u003e, depending on which is higher.",
                    "SS2_INTERACTABLE_DROPPOD_CONTEXT":  "Open the pod?",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_BLOODLETTING_DESC":  "Consume \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e25%\u003c/style\u003e of your health to inspire \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003efear\u003c/style\u003e in nearby enemies and\u003c/style\u003e gain 3 \u003ccolor=#29e5f2\u003eIon Charges\u003c/color\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_PRIMARY_NAME":  "balls",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_ADVERSITY_NAME":  "Artifact of Adversity",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ARMEDBACKPACK_DESC":  "Chance on taking damage to fire a missile for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e base damage. Chance scales with damage taken.",
                    "SS2_BORG_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Jet Thrusters",
