                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_UNCLAIMED_REMOVED_2P":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003eA deal was struck. Claim your birthright.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_TEMPEST2_NAME":  "Tempest +2",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_SUPERFIRE":  "Infernal {0}",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_GOOLAKE":  "A view of the gate.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_BOSSATTACK_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, apply 8 or more stacks of Gouge to a single target at once.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_FIELDACCELERATOR_NAME":  "Going Long",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_NAME":  "Relic of Extinction",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_75_DECREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "-75% Damage Received",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKEFROST_NAME":  "ORDER: Strike PSI",
                    "SS2_TRADER_POPUP_TEXT":  "Offer an item to the trader?",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DORMANTFUNGUS_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eHeals\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e of your health every second \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ewhile sprinting\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STICKYOVERLOADER_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_NAME":  "Chirr",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_OBJECTIVE":  "{0} \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eBirthright(s)\u003c/style\u003e unclaimed",
                    "SS2_UNLOCKABLE_LOG_LAMP":  "Logbook: Follower",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONJUGGERNAUT_DESC":  "Swing your ion axe for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1700% damage\u003c/style\u003e while held. Activating begins slowly consuming \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eIon Manipulator charges\u003c/style\u003e to project ion armor.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_HAVOC_DESC":  "Events happen sooner and more frequently. Storms are permanent.",
                    "SS2_RULEBOOK_EMPTY":  "No customizable rules found!",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SLIDE_DESC":  "As Nemesis Mercenary, complete a stage without leaving the ground.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_WHITEFLAG_DESC":  "Place a white flag that \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003edisables skill usage\u003c/style\u003e within \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}m\u003c/style\u003e. Lasts \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{1} seconds\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_AGARTHAN_BODY_NAME":  "Agarthan",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SKATEBOARD_LORE":  "Wheels, rolling against unhewn stone. Unrefined, uncoordinated technique- irresponsible and careless in equal measure.\n\n\"You are doing it wrong.\"\n\n\"I am doing this as I please! This is an art, you know, Brother.\"\n\n\"You\u0027ve failed countless times already.\"\n\n\"We\u0027ll see.\"\n\nFocused eyes, darting as stars reflecting the sky. Lightning flashes against the remote landscape in the distance. Twinkling thunderbolts catching a stray eye. A single lapse of focus, then an impact. A frustrated scoff. Glares, mutual and infuriated, sharp enough to cut through the gap in the air preceding oncoming thunder.\n\n\"I\u0027m beginning to have doubts, Brother.\"\n\n\"..well, I\u0027ve yet to give up! How could I have failed?\"\n\nImpact, skidding quick enough to sear against the kicked-up dust. Shaky limbs, rising from the ground. Defiance. Potential energy, mounting into heat and purpose, tangible in the air. Suffocating tension, louder than thunder. It all comes crashing down.\n\n\"Another failure.\"\n\n\"..you know, I don\u0027t believe I\u0027ve failed once, Brother. There\u0027s something to be said of art about the simple act of learning.\"\n\n\"You HAVE failed! Each and every time you have tried you have failed, and I have attempted to teach you- but you do not listen. I grow tired of teaching and tired of watching!\"\n\nWheels begin to roll against stone again. They hum and kick like an organ attuned to the pulse of the Earth underfoot, barely holding on.\n\n\"You incessantly add your own additions to even my simplest instructions..\"\n\nForward movement. The thrill of velocity in one\u0027s chest. Of feeling your blood and senses rush back, jostled by inertia. A reminder of truly being alive.\n\n\"When you\u0027re done playing with all this, allow me to demonstrate what I\u0027ve tried to teach.\"\n\nUncontrollable energy, wild and frenzied- forces converging together at last. A perfect storm.\nRotation, freed of an axis and speed- that essential rush of heat and velocity.\nLightning. Raw energy, full of potential- now fully realized.\nJoy and astonishment and elation. Shock. Satisfaction. Excitement. A third voice, calling out impatiently over the Venusian storm.\n\n\"Come in, boys- dinner\u0027s ready and it\u0027s no weather to be skateboarding in!\"",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_MIDAS_LORE":  "\"What do you think it means?\"\n\nThey both had been wondering. She was the first to ask aloud.\n\n\"My... Ideal Day Alone Starts?\" He gave her a toothy smile.\n\n\"Memphis Is Dying Again Stephan.\"\n\n\"Mitochondria Is Defeated At Six.\"\n\n\"Mortician Ignores Death And Sighs.\"\n\n\"Poetic, that one.\" He scratched his chin. \"Wanna open it up?\"\n\n\"Hell no!\"",
                    "SS2_ITEM_UNIVERSALCHARGER_LORE":  "Supports UESB-A through UESB-ZZ bla bla bla",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_BODY_LORE":  "why are there WARDENs in space",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_LORE":  "yehaw",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_DIARY_DESC":  "Reach level 20.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MALICE_DESC":  "Your attacks deal \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e TOTAL damage to up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e additional enemies within \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{3}m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he returned, legacy lost forever.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_25_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players take 125% damage.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DROIDHEAD_NAME":  "Droid Head",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_PRIMARY_CANNON_NAME":  "Unmaker",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SECONDARY_KNIFE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eBleeding.\u003c/style\u003e Throw a knife for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e100% damage\u003c/style\u003e. \n\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eSlayer.\u003c/style\u003e Get close to rip it out and deal \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_SECONDARY_DESC":  "Swing and throw a boomeranging, piercing hatchet for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e240% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Hits \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e5 times per second\u003c/style\u003e while in the air.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTBULB_PICKUP":  "Reduces skill cooldowns by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e8%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(-8% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. Taking damage to below \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e25% health\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ebreaks\u003c/style\u003e this item.",
                    "SS2_PEDESTAL_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_MALICE_NAME":  "Malicious",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_GRAB_NAME":  "Abduct",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_LORE":  "???",
                    "SS2_ITEM_CRYPTICSOURCE_PICKUP":  "Sprinting charges up a damaging burst of energy.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_CRYPTICSOURCE_NAME":  "Cryptic Source",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_NAME":  "Dynamite Toss",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Bloodbath",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DROIDHEAD_LORE":  "Order: Security Robot\nTracking Number: 1138***\nEstimated Delivery: 5/14/2056\nShipping Method: Priority / Fragile\nShipping Address: RaCom Robotics, Asimov, Mars\nShipping Details:\n\nThis was one of the few complete bits we could salvage from those stolen security robots... That militant group on Pluto had stolen a bunch of those ER-14s, and had been using \u0027em at their bases for a while. This one specifically, ER-14XPC5VVUFF, lines up with the ones you\u0027d tried to recall a while back. I don\u0027t know this history, I just know there was a big bounty for whoever could find the remains for this batch. There\u0027s other remnants, too, but they\u0027re much less complete... Shouldn\u0027t be any danger anymore, at least. Gimme a heads up if you want those shipped your way, too.\n",
                    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_DESCRIPTION":  "A companion bought with gold that will follow the survivor at a close distance, \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eshocking\u003c/style\u003e enemies, interrupting and stunning them.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_100_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players take 200% damage.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DETRITIVETREMATODE_PICKUP":  "Low health enemies receive damage over time until death.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_BACKTHRUSTER_DESC":  "For {0} seconds, rapidly build up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{1} movement speed\u003c/style\u003e when moving in a straight line.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_DROP_DESCRIPTION":  "Release your victim to deal \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1500% damage\u003c/style\u003e in an area on impact.",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SECONDARY_LASER_NAME":  "Rising Star",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COMPOSITEINJECTOR_NAME":  "Composite Injector",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RAINBOWROOT_NAME":  "Rainbow Root",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_50_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players deal 150% damage.",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, ",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_POISONOUSGLAND_NAME":  "Sooo Toxic",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXDAZING_NAME":  "Focal Obfuscator",
                    "SS2_CHIRRHELPER_NAME":  "Chirr\u0027s Friendship",
                    "SS2_EVENT_FOG_START":  "A thick fog builds up...",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_EXPLOSIVE_BOW_NAME":  "Explosive Bolt",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FORK_LORE":  "\"You can\u0027t be serious... Look, I know we said we need everything we can get to survive, but you have to realize I wasn\u0027t literal about it!\"\n\nHe held up the silver instrument, a questioning look on his face. \"What do you mean? What if we need to fight off a monster?\"\n\nA brief silence.\n\n\"Please, we\u0027ve both seen the creatures on this planet. Don\u0027t tell me you think that\u0027d be enough to fight off anything here.\"\n\nHe shrugged. \"You never know\", he replied, as he slid the fork into his pocket.\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_NAME":  "Bleedout",
                    "SS2_MAP_VOIDSHOP_LORE":  "Void Shop Temp Lore",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_ALT_NAME":  "Coin Toss",
