                    "SS2_EVENT_GENERICNEMESIS_START":  "You feel an ominous presence...\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Bandit carefully positions himself via camouflage technology to wrangle foes and cull crowds. \n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Show no mercy.",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_USE_MESSAGE":  "\u003cstyle=cEvent\u003eThe Ethereal Sapling has activated!\u003c/style\u003e",
