                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_EXPLOSIVE_BOW_DESC":  "Swap the arrow of your next \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eprimary\u003c/style\u003e with a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003estunning\u003c/style\u003e arrow that explodes shortly after impact for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERHEAL_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eHeal\u003c/style\u003e nearby allies for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e6%\u003c/style\u003e of their \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003emaximum health\u003c/style\u003e every second, and also grant \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e50 armor\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e+20% attack speed\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e12 seconds\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_CYBORG2_DEFAULT":  "Default",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SECONDARY_CONCUSSION_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eGouging\u003c/style\u003e. Fire a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003epiercing\u003c/style\u003e sword beam for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_PRIMARY_NAME":  "Gunslinger",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_WEATHERRADIO_DESC":  "As Commando, kill a Stormborn boss on Monsoon difficulty.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_SPITBOMB_NAME":  "Soothing Venom",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_UNIVERSALCHARGER_DESC":  "As Engineer, kill 400 enemies with your turrets.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_URANIUMHORSESHOE_PICKUP":  "Run faster, jump higher.",
                    "SS2_EVENT_EMPYREANSPAWN_START":  "Powerful energies begin to harmonize...",
                    "SS2_EVENT_THUNDERSTORM_START":  "\u003csprite name=\"CloudRight\"\u003e\t A storm is approaching...",
                    "SS2_ITEM_PORTABLEREACTOR_PICKUP":  "Become invincible when entering a stage.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_ROCKFRUIT_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eTransmute\u003c/style\u003e a \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003erandom\u003c/style\u003e item from your inventory into another of the \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003esame tier\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_MASTERY_NAME":  "Chirr: Mastery",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he vanished, escaping the inevitable.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_25_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+25% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_NAME":  "Striking Rush",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RAINBOWROOT_LORE":  "What rainbow could possibly come from such rain?",
                    "SS2_EXPANSION_NAME":  "Starstorm 2",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_PYRO_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Pyro: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTNINGONKILL_NAME":  "Man-o\u0027-War",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ICETOOL_DESC":  "While \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003etouching a wall\u003c/style\u003e, gain \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e+1\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+1 per stack)\u003c/style\u003e extra jump.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_DESC":  "All attacks strike \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+1 per stack)\u003c/style\u003e additional time for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e TOTAL damage. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eConsecutive strikes\u003c/style\u003e to the same enemy increase damage dealt by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e, up to a maximum of \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}%\u003c/style\u003e TOTAL damage dealt. \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eReduce attack speed and increase skill cooldowns by {0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(-{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DORMANTFUNGUS_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eDocumentation from Research Station Rook\n\nSpecimen-18305 Week 3 Notes\u003c/style\u003e\n\nThis is one of the more odd samples we\u0027ve found. This fungus has seemed to grow on nearly everything in the building if we let it. The walls, floors, ceiling. They seem to have a preference for things that have been moving. Our clothes, doors, and even some machinery. We will continue to monitor this behavior.\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eSpecimen-18305 Week 5 Notes\u003c/style\u003e\n\nThe subject has continued to attach itself to things around the lab. We\u0027ve noted that it becomes healthier the more it moves with its attached object. Tests seem to indicate it subsists off of the heat created by movements, taken in by its roots. We will attempt to transplant it to a consistently moving machine and monitor its health.\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eSpecimen-18305 Week 8 Notes\u003c/style\u003e\n\nWe\u0027ve left the sample attached to an old model of piston from the lab. In case of any damage, we had intended to dispose of it regardless. We had attached it and left it running the previous 3 weeks. Most curiously, the piston was assumed to break down in this time frame. However, it would seem the subject has created a symbiotic relationship with the machine. We will continue to monitor this behavior for more negative effects, and potential other uses for this specimen.\n",
                    "SS2_SKIN_MERCENARY_NEMESIS":  "Ballistic",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eexploding\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "Crime has a new enemy",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SECONDARY_MINES_DESCRIPTION":  "Place a mine that repeatedly \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eshocks\u003c/style\u003e and \u003ccolor=#42f5b3\u003ePrimes\u003c/color\u003e nearby targets. Can place up to 3.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION":  "Chirr \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ejumps higher\u003c/style\u003e and can \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ehover\u003c/style\u003e by holding the jump key. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eChirr is always sprinting while hovering.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_PYRO_UTILITY_DESC":  "Consume \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003eheat\u003c/color\u003e to charge up an explosive jump for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e350% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Can be \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ereactivated\u003c/style\u003e to hover in the air.",
                    "SS2_TRADER_QUALITY_BESTEST":  "\u003cb\u003eMost Wanted\u003c/b\u003e",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_50_DECREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "-50% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_PRESSURIZEDCANISTER_PICKUP":  "Launch yourself into the air, and temporarily gain an additional extra jump that expires upon touching the ground.",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_UNCLAIMED_DEAD":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003eThe dead have unfinished business; claim what was sought.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_DELUGE_DESC":  "",
                    "SS2_EVENT_BLAZINGELITE_START":  "The sun starts blazing...",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONELITEKILL_DESC":  "Elites have a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e6%\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cStack\u003e (+2% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e chance to drop an \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eitem\u003c/style\u003e on kill.",
                    "SS2_EVENT_ASHSTORM_END":  "The ashes begins to settle...",
