                    "SS2_CYBORG2_UTILITY_TRAP_NAME":  "Repurpose",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_BLACKBEACH":  "Gazing down upon the island.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_EXECUTION_NAME":  "Execution",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, battered to the core of hope.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_ITEM_JETBOOTS_DESC":  "Gain \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e+1 extra jump\u003c/style\u003e that \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eignites\u003c/style\u003e enemies for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e base damage in a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e radius. Recharges \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{3}\u003c/style\u003e seconds after landing.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_TOOLBOT_GRANDMASTERY":  "Construct",
                    "SS2_BORG_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION":  "Holding the Jump key allows you to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eslow your descent\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_PYRO_PASSIVE_DESC":  "The Pyro is \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eimmune\u003c/style\u003e to burn, and gains \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003eheat\u003c/color\u003e from nearby burning enemies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BABYTOYS_PICKUP":  "Lose {0} levels while keeping all stats.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_LORE":  "Hey! You! In this file! You probably shouldn\u0027t be here... Keep quiet, okay?",
                    "SS2_SKILL_DISABLED_NAME":  "Disabled",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_SECONDARY_SHIELD_DESC":  "Raise your shield to block gaining X% armor, and Y% movement speed decrease. Blocking an attack within the first 0.5s of activation parries the attack and empowers your next skill. Your primary becomes a shield bash and jumping while holding your shield rolls you instead.",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SECONDARY_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eIgnite\u003c/style\u003e. Consume \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003eheat\u003c/color\u003e to burn enemies for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e451% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e. At \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e70% heat\u003c/color\u003e, leave a trail of fire for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e200% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERREGEN_DESCRIPTION":  "Temporarily increase the rate at which Stress decreases for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e15 seconds\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SECONDARY_NAME":  "Hazard Reduction",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HOTTESTSAUCE_NAME":  "Hottest Sauce",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eHeavy\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eExecuting.\u003c/style\u003e Launch into the air and slam downwards with a massive ion axe for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SANTAHAT_LORE":  "Merry Chirristmas!",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SPECIAL_SUBMISSION_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Fire repeatedly for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6x80% damage\u003c/style\u003e per shot. The number of shots increases with attack speed.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_HUNTERSSIGIL_DESC":  "Deal 1,000 damage or more with a single critical strike.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SECONDARY_SHOOT_NAME":  "Single Tap",
                    "SS2_MAP_VOIDSHOP_SUBTITLE":  "Somewhere in the Void",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Invigorate",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFECHELON_LORE":  "No no Youngling, you are here too soon! I haven\u0027t the time to prepare. Please...Come back later.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTBULB_NAME":  "Miracle Lightbulb",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he returned, luck finally running out.",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, newfound sense of humanity within.",
                    "SS2_NEMHUNTRESS2_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "Cunning Stalker",
                    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_DESC":  "Upon recieving \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e of your \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003emaximum health\u003c/style\u003e in \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003edamage\u003c/style\u003e, unleash a devastating \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eblackout\u003c/color\u003e, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003einstantly killing\u003c/style\u003e all \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003enon-Boss enemies\u003c/style\u003e caught in it.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FIELDACCELERATOR_PICKUP":  "Killing enemies reduces Teleporter charge time and increases teleporter range.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG_MASTERY_DESC":  "As Cyborg, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_PEDESTAL_CONTEXT":  "Use Pedestal",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_COGNATION_NAME":  "Trial of Cognation",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SPECIAL_SUBMISSION_NAME":  "Submission",
                    "SS2_MULE_PUNCH_DESC":  "Punch enemies for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e330% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SPECIAL_BOSS_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eGouging.\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eCharge up\u003c/style\u003e, then \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003edash forward\u003c/style\u003e and unleash a devastating barrage of up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0} slashes\u003c/style\u003e that deal up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}% damage each\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eThe number of slashes increases with attack speed\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_DEFAULT":  "Default",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTBULB_DESC":  "Reduced skill cooldowns. Breaks at low health.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG_DESC":  "Complete an Ethereal Teleporter event.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DROIDHEAD_DESC":  "Killing an elite enemy spawns a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eSecurity Drone\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% base damage per stack)\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}s\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}s per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. Spawned drones \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003einherit the elite type\u003c/style\u003e of the slain elite.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "Ferryman of the Damned",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_SPECIAL_BANNER_DESC":  "Leap and slam a banner that slows down enemies, projectiles, grants \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eX% movement speed\u003c/style\u003e, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eY% attack speed\u003c/style\u003e, for yourself and your allies.",
                    "SS2_VOIDROCK_USED_NAME":  "Vacant Dirt Pile",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, an empty shell of armor drenched in blood.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eWelcome to DataScraper (v3.1.53 - beta branch)\n$ Scraping memory... done.\n$ Resolving... done.\n$ Combing for relevant data...\n$ Combing for relevant data - continued...\n$ Com-bi-- fo- re--vant da-a-a-a-a-...\n$ ...\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eWhat are you looking for\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eYou already know what happened to them\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eso why bother digging up graves\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eknowing you will only find misery\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eIs it hope\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eDo you hope they are still alive\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eBecause your hope is well placed\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eThey are alive\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003eand you will meet them again\u003c/color\u003e\n$ \u003ccolor=#FFCCED\u003e\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eVery soon\u003c/link\u003e\u003c/color\u003e\n$\nError!\nOutputting error log...\n\u003c/style\u003e\nThe data is either heavily encrypted or irreversibly corrupted. Consider external options before scraping again.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_LEAVES_NAME":  "Razor Leaves",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_BLEED":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eBleed\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDeal \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e240%\u003c/style\u003e base damage over 3s. \u003ci\u003eBleed can stack.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_WARN_MESSAGE_2P":  "\u003cstyle=cEvent\u003eYou have primed the Ethereal Sapling..\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_RECHARGING2":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eRecharging\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eThis skill can recharge additional stocks by holding the button or killing enemies. Additional stocks increase maximum capacity.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_DESC":  "Slain monsters leave a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003esoul\u003c/style\u003e which has a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per unsuccessful roll, resetting on success)\u003c/style\u003e chance to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003espawn an item\u003c/style\u003e on pickup.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CAPTAIN_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Captain: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_PYRO_MASTERY_DESC":  "As Pyro, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_NAME":  "Executioner",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_GILDED":  "Gilded {0}",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_COMMANDO_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Commando, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or Harder.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERNULL_NAME":  "Refresh Order",
                    "SS2_PYRO_PRIMARY_DESC":  "\u003ccolor=#D78326\u003eHeat up\u003c/color\u003e by burning enemies for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e270% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e. At \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e70% heat\u003c/color\u003e, gains a chance to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eIgnite\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SPECIAL_SCEPBOSS_NAME":  "Judgement Cut",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_PRESSURIZEDCANISTER_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eLaunch\u003c/style\u003e yourself into the air. Gain \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e1 extra jump\u003c/style\u003e that expires if not used before landing.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "Royal Guard",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_TEMPEST_NAME":  "Tempest",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BANEFLASK_NAME":  "Bane Flask",
                    "SS2_ITEM_X4_PICKUP":  "Slightly decreases secondary skill cooldown and grants healing upon using it.",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_NEWTSPEECH":  "The shopkeeper whispers, \"{1}\"",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LOWQUALITYSPEAKERS_LORE":  "Return: A-AMP 25-Watt All Purpose Speaker\nTracking Number: 629********\nEstimated Delivery: 03/14/2055\nShipping Method: Priority\nShipping Address 444 Anthem Ln., Twin Cities, Earth\nReason For Return:\n\nSorry to be a burden, mate, but when I unpackaged it and plugged it in to test it, the audio came out...fuzzy? Staticky? I-it\u0027s hard to describe. If I had to guess, it got damaged in transit. Guess I\u0027m glad I sprung for the warranty.\n\nRefund:\nReplace: X",
                    "SS2_ITEM_URANIUMHORSESHOE_DESC":  "Increases \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ejump height\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DIARY_CONSUMED_PICKUP":  "They\u0027ll totally make a movie out of this.",
                    "SS2_WIKI_ITEM_FORMAT":  "\n[“{0}“] = {{\n\tRarity = “{1}“,\n\tQuote = “{2}“,\n\tDesc = “{3}“,\n\tCategory = {{ “{4}“ }},\n\tUnlock = “{5}“,\n\tCorrupt = “{6}“, \n\tUncorrupt = “{7}“,\n\t ID = ,\n\tStats = {{\n\t\t {{\n\t\t\tStat = ““,\n\t\t\tValue = ““,\n\t\t\tStack = ““,\n\t\t\tAdd = ““\n\t\t}}\n\t}},\n\tLocalizationInternalName = “{8}“\n\t}}",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DIARY_PICKUP":  "Level up when entering a stage. Consumed on use.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HITLIST_DESC":  "Every \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e30\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(-20% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e seconds, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003emark\u003c/style\u003e an enemy. Killing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003emarked\u003c/style\u003e enemies increases your \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edamage permanently\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e2%\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_UNLOCKABLE_LOG_MIMIC":  "Logbook: Security Chest",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_NAME":  "Executioner",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SPECIAL_ALT_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eCombusting\u003c/style\u003e. Fire a shotgun burst for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e8x50% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SHIELDGATE_PICKUP":  "Killing an enemy permanently increases your shield.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERLIGHTNING_NAME":  "Eye of the Storm (shouldnt this be stormborn?)",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HOTTESTSAUCE_PICKUP":  "Activating your equipment ignites nearby enemies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_OPTIONFROMCHEST_NAME":  "OptionFromChest",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, lighting up a fresh smoke.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SLIDE_NAME":  "Nemesis Mercenary: Grounded",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTBULB_CONSUMED_DESC":  "Remnant of a bright idea.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_25_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+25% Damage Received",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_VOID":  "Condemned {0}",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXVOID_NAME":  "Condemned Bond",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_UTILITY_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eRearming\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eDisappear\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eteleport\u003c/style\u003e a short distance. Can store up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e3\u003c/style\u003e charges.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ARMEDBACKPACK_NAME":  "Armed Backpack",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG_NAME":  "Powered Up",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTNINGONKILL_PICKUP":  "Discharge electricity on kill.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONELITEKILL_NAME":  "ItemOnEliteKill",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BORG_MASTERY_NAME":  "Cyborg: Mastery",
                    "SS2_ELITE_ULTRA_SUBTITLE":  "Overruling Denouement",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SPECIAL_DETONATE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eBoom.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_MULE_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so it vanished, finally put out of commission.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GALVANICCORE_NAME":  "Galvanic Core",
                    "SS2_GHOUL_BODY_NAME":  "AHHHHHHHHHH!!!!!!!!",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_SHIPGRAVEYARD":  "Within a deep ravine.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_NEMCOMMANDO_MASTERY":  "Wasp",
                    "SS2_ITEM_WATCHMETRONOME_DESC":  "While not sprinting, charge up to a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e increase to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003esprint speed\u003c/style\u003e that decays over \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{1}s\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}s per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. While active, your skills can be used while sprinting.",
                    "SS2_HERO_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "Umbra of the Bulwark",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_UNCLAIMED_2P":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003eYou lack what you seek.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXEMPYREAN_PICKUP":  "Become an aspect of existence.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ICETOOL_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_ITEM_JETBOOTS_PICKUP":  "Gain an explosive jump!",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MOLTENCOIN_PICKUP":  "Chance to burn and gain gold on hit.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_HAVOC_NAME":  "Trial of Havoc",
                    "SS2_ITEM_X4_NAME":  "X-4 Stimulant",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SECONDARY_SHOOT_DESCRIPTION":  "Shoot an enemy for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e150% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Reloads \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eall\u003c/style\u003e at once.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_CLASSIC":  "Nostalgic",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so she left, carrying new life in her spirit.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXETHEREAL_PICKUP":  "Become an aspect of the unknown.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_POISONOUSGLAND_PICKUP":  "Debuffs make enemies miss their attacks.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FORK_DESC":  "Increase your base damage by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_NAME":  "Competitive Exclusion Principle",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SPECIAL_DETONATE_NAME":  "Detonate",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_EMPOWERING":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eEmpowering\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003e\u003ccolor=#fa78f3\u003eImproves\u003c/color\u003e your next skill use.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MAXHPONKILL_PICKUP":  "Killing an enemy permanently increases your maximum health.",
                    "SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_PUNCH_CALIBRATED":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eCalibrated\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/style=cSub\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eSlam the ground in front of you, dealing higher damage and sending out a shockwave. (%s tbd)\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_RECHARGING":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eRecharging\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eKilling enemies restores charges of this skill, depending on the strength of the slain enemy. Doubled charges with kills from Execution.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_BEFRIEND_SCEPTER_NAME":  "Mesmerize",
                    "SS2_SKIN_COMMANDO_ALT3":  "Praetor",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_TOOLBOT_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As MUL-T, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or Harder.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SKATEBOARD_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eSprint\u003c/style\u003e in \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eany direction\u003c/style\u003e. Using a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eskill\u003c/style\u003e grants a buff which provides \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e+{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{4}\u003c/style\u003e seconds, up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{2}\u003c/style\u003e stacks.",
                    "SS2_MAP_VOIDSHOP_NAME":  "Hidden Realm: Stranger\u0027s Hideout",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONBOSSKILL_DESC":  "Bosses drop an \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eitem\u003c/style\u003e on kill. \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(Item rarity increases per stack)\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_UTILITY_BACKDASH_DESCRIPTION":  "",
                    "SS2_RUNSHROOM_BODY_LORE":  "We awoke in a panic, our tent ablaze. Our equipment a molten mass of the periodic table.\n\n\"H-hey, over there! That thing!\"\n\nIt was so small, it looked like it could be a bug under our shoe, yet the mess it made... There was no other way.\n\n\"Stay here, I\u0027m gonna go squeeze that thing to a fuckin\u0027 pulp.\"\n\nI sat there and watched as my crew lept like frogs at the small fungi, unable to even graze its surface. Profanities like a siren in the air.\n\nOur efforts were fruitless. I signaled for the crew to return to aid in the dowsing of the flames.\n\n\"Pipe down and get over here! The fire ain\u0027t dyin\u0027 by itself! The bastard\u0027s like a roach, you won\u0027t catch it!\"\n\nThe damages weren\u0027t covered.",
                    "SS2_AMBUSH_MESSAGE_DOUBLE":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003e{0} has been ambushed by {1}s and {2}s\u003c/color\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CAPTAIN_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Captain, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or Harder.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_TOYSOLDIERS_NAME":  "Assemble",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKESHOCK_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eShocking\u003c/style\u003e. Aim a Microbot and fire a laser, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eexploding\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e900% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_LEASH_NAME":  "Natural Sync",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_HAIDARA_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eShocking\u003c/style\u003e. Discharge a thunderbolt in front for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e440% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ERRATICGADGET_DESC":  "Your lightning strikes \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003etwice\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e chance on hit to fire \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003echain lightning\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e TOTAL damage on up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e targets.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_GRENADE_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando: Completely Corrupted",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_UTILITY_BLINK_NAME":  "Dispatch",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NEEDLES_NAME":  "Needles",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_BODY_NAME":  "Cyborg",
                    "SS2_ELITE_EMPYREAN_SUBTITLE":  "Devout Prescience of Petrichor V",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NKOTASHERITAGE_PICKUP":  "Receive an item upon level up.",
                    "SS2_BORG_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, with a broken arm and no spare parts.",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SUBTITLE":  "Professional Ecocide",
                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_SUPERLIGHTNING":  "Supercharged {0}",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_PRESSURIZEDCANISTER_LORE":  "Order: Pressured Air Canister (24)\nTracking Number: 182*****\nEstimated Delivery: 06/29/2056\nShipping Method: Standard / Fragile\nShipping Address: Tri-City Gas Shipment Center, Tri-City, Earth\nShipping Details:\n\nThis is the, uh, fifth, is it now? Fifth order of pressurized air canisters to this address. Now, I\u0027m not going to judge, I mean, maybe you didn\u0027t know you\u0027d need more canisters, for, uh, four times in a row, but, like, you do know you save quite a bit when you buy in bulk, right?\n\nWhatever, man. I mean, I don\u0027t really know what you\u0027d need with a hundred and twenty total air canisters over the span of about two months, but I guess you do you.\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_PICKUP":  "\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eCan you hear them...? They\u0027re coming...\u003c/link\u003e",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SPECIAL_DESC":  "\u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e70% Heat\u003c/color\u003e. Launch a fireball for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e800% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Ignited enemies increase the blast radius, then explode for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_PICKUP":  "A black hole follows you that deals extreme damage, BUT it can damage you.",
                    "SS2_MULE_DESCRIPTION":  "Seriously this is a very rough early prototype of an old MULE design for SS2. A full rework is planned, Enjoy it as a novelty, but its buggy.",
                    "SS2_MULE_JUMP_NAME":  "Relocate",
                    "SS2_EVENT_GLACIALELITE_END":  "The sharp, frigid air settles down...",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_MERCENARY_NEMESISSKIN_NAME":  "Mercenary: Vengeful Deserter",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_PYRO_DESC":  "",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SECONDARY_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Arm your cane rifle, then fire a shot for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e680% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BANEFLASK_LORE":  "the gray hurts ow!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!",
                    "SS2_EVENT_TARSTORM_START":  "\u003csprite name=\"CloudRight\"\u003e\t Tar rains down from the sky...",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_MASTERY_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando: Mastery",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_PRIMARY_BLADE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eGouging\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile\u003c/style\u003e. Slice enemies in front for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e160% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_WATCHMETRONOME_PICKUP":  "Charge up a movement speed boost while not sprinting.",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SECONDARY_DESCRIPTION":  "toss dynamite figure out #s later",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GALVANICCORE_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{4} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e chance on hit to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estun\u003c/style\u003e. Stunned enemies apply \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003erazed\u003c/style\u003e to enemies within \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{5}m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{6}m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e, reducing their \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003emaximum health\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e, \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edamage\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}%\u003c/style\u003e, and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{3}%\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_X4_LORE":  "Order: Stimulant (X-4)\nTracking Number: 369*****\nEstimated Delivery: 4/12/2057\nShipping Method: Priority\nShipping Address: Romeo 33, Batang Ai National Park, Earth\nShipping Details:\n\nEncased, including manual. Does the machine show symptoms of a 540? If so you may want to avoid using above 100ml of stimulant.\n\nCheers.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HOTTESTSAUCE_DESC":  "Activating your equipment \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eignites\u003c/style\u003e enemies within \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}m\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}\u003c/style\u003e seconds, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e150% base damage\u003c/style\u003e plus \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e100% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+50% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Invigorate",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_HEADBUTT_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Headbutt enemies in front of you \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_DROIDDRONE_DESCRIPTION":  "A temporary companion created when holding Droid Head and killing elites that will follow the survivor at a close distance, shooting nearby enemies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_CHUNGUS_DESC":  "After standing still for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e1\u003c/style\u003e second, create a zone that \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eheals\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e5.5%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+2.75% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e of your \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003ehealth\u003c/style\u003e every second to all allies within \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e3m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+1.5m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsVoid\u003eCorrupts all Dormant Fungi\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BLOODTESTER_DESC":  "Heal for 5,000 health in a single run.",
                    "SS2_EVENT_TARSTORM_END":  "The tar begins to settle...",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXULTRA_PICKUP":  "",
                    "SS2_RULEBOOK_NAME":  "Rules",
                    "SS2_EXPANSION_DESC":  "Adds content from the \u0027Starstorm 2\u0027 mod into the game.",
                    "SS2_MULE_PASSIVE_DRONE_DESC":  "Taking damage to below \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e25% health\u003c/style\u003eactivates your personal \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eRepair Drone\u003c/style\u003e, healing for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e50%\u003c/style\u003e of your health. Has a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e60\u003c/style\u003e second cooldown.",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_UNCLAIMED_REMOVED":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003eA deal was struck. {0} must claim their birthright.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_BODY_NAME":  "Chirr",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_UTILITY_SLIDE_NAME":  "Devitalize",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_DAMPCAVESIMPLE":  "Neighbor to the caretaker.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_PICKUP":  "\u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003e... At what cost?...\u003c/link\u003e",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_DEFAULT_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players deal 100% damage.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SCRAPFROMCHEST_NAME":  "ScrapFromChest",
                    "SS2_MISSED_DAMAGE_HITMARKER":  "MISSED!",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_LORE":  "Death is inevitable. It comes for us all. Some may try to evade it, or run from it. But death arrives all the same. Death, however, is simply the cost of war. And death in glorious combat is one of the best deaths a man could ask for.\n\nBut, as always, some would seek to run from death. We call them by many names. Deserters, cowards, turncoats. Each and every one of them, traitors to the cause. These traitors must be punished for their crime. And that punishment: in an ironic twist, is the very thing they tried to avoid.\n\nDeath will come for them. Not as a robed spectre with a scythe. Not in a trench coat, holding a revolver. Not as a sickness, nor the wear of time. No. For them, death will come bearing lustrous battlegarb, with service pistol loaded, and ion manipulators fully charged.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STICKYOVERLOADER_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e chance to attach a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eliving bomb\u003c/style\u003e that gains \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{1}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e base damage and a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{3}m\u003c/style\u003e blast radius per hit, up to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e20\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+5 per stack)\u003c/style\u003e times. The bomb explodes after \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1\u003c/style\u003e second without growing.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_CHIRR_MASTERY":  "Nocturnal",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_SUPERTYPHOON2_NAME":  "Super Typhoon +2",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_SUBTITLE":  "Blackened Outlaw",
                    "SS2_EVENT_BLIZZARD_START":  "\u003csprite name=\"CloudRight\"\u003e\t A snowstorm is approaching..",
                    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_NAME":  "Condemned Bond",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_NEMESIS_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, defeat Commando\u0027s vestige.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_CYBORG2_MASTERY":  "[temp]CyborgMastery",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXKINETIC_NAME":  "Boundless Pressure",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MALICE_PICKUP":  "Attacks spread damage to nearby enemies.",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_CONSECRATION_NAME":  "Consecration",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_50_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+50% Damage Received",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_PASSIVE_DESC":  "Killing enemies inflicted with \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003efear\u003c/style\u003e reduces all skill cooldowns by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e1 second\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_MULE_SPIN_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eOverclocking\u003c/style\u003e. Rapidly spin, gradually increasing \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003emovement speed\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eincreasing armor\u003c/style\u003e while dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e100% damage\u003c/style\u003e per rotation.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_BEASTMASTER_NAME":  "Chirr: Beastmaster",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERICE_PICKUP":  "Become a harbinger of ice.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MAXHPONKILL_DESC":  "Killing an enemy increases your \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003ehealth permanently\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e2\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+1 per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_GOLEMPLAINS2":  "Where the structure meets the earth.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_CLONE_DESCRIPTION":  "Summon a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eclone\u003c/style\u003e behind a target that \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003ecopies your abilities\u003c/style\u003e. Recast to dash to it, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e800% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_UTILITY_DODGE_NAME":  "Tactical Roll",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_HEADBUTT_NAME":  "Chirr: Long Live the Queen",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_BACKTHRUSTER_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eAudio transcription complete from signal echoes. Assigning generic tokens.\u003c/style\u003e\n\nMAN 1: This is a terrible idea, you know.\n[rattling metal]\n\nMAN 2: You say that about every idea I have.\n\nMAN 1: Because all of your ideas are terrible.\n\n[engine sputtering]\n\nMAN 2: Rrgh, oh, c\u0027mon, then! You were working fine just a minute ago.\n\nMAN 1: Maybe it knows it\u0027s attached to your back, and not to a piece of cargo.\n\nMAN 2: Oh, good point! I bet these have a safety on them of some sort... Ah, ther it is.\n\n[click]\n\nMAN 1: I... Shouldn\u0027t have said anything.\n\nMAN 2: Nah, this is great! Alright, count me down.\n\nMAN 1 : Ugh... Alright. Three-\n\n[thruster blasting off]\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eEnd of requested transcript.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_NAME":  "Shock Drone",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NEEDLES_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eUES Delivery Incident Report ID 219560163 found.\n\nPlaying...\u003c/style\u003e\n\n\"The delivery personnel Will Stetson, number 604, was admitted to the medical bay aboard the UES [REDACTED], about 22 hours ago, due to complications related to handling aberrant package behavior.\n\nWhile doing his rounds, Will noticed one of the chests suddenly thudded, rather quite loudly, behind him. Concerned that someone might have tried to ship a living animal under Standard protocol, he felt the need to investigate. Instead, what was in the chest was a small plastic package containing a large number of particularly sizable sewing needles, obviously packaged far too tightly for any amount of safety.\n\nFinally, and, likely in a lapse of judgement, Will decided to touch the package. This caused the package to suddenly rupture into his general direction, leaving his upper front side covered in deep gashes. He\u0027s lucky someone found him quickly. He seems to be doing fine, but will be recovering from the shock and loss of blood for a while.\"\n\nEnd of report.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COFFEEBAG_NAME":  "Coffee Bag",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_LORE":  "He lays to rest by a fire, setting the weapons he carries within an arm\u0027s reach. Checking his surroundings, hoping the cave he hid in would be enough shelter. Some would say it is not wise to be overly cautious. He would say, \u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003ethey have not seen enough\u003c/link\u003e.\n\nThe service pistol he got when he enlisted. Well used, dirtied, and loved. It\u0027s brought him through thick and thin, no matter the circumstance. Some would say that only a fool would trust their weapon. He would say, \u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eyour weapon is all you can trust.\u003c/link\u003e\n\nThe blade of a fallen brother of war. Picked from what he could scavenge of the last of humanity he\u0027s seen. Some would say it keeps their spirits united. He would say, \u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eit keeps their spirits from joining for as long as possible.\u003c/link\u003e\n\nThe loads of cargo that landed with him. Each item picked from a chest, keeping him alive in one way or another. Dozens of shipments to anyone but him. Some would say they aren\u0027t his to take. He would say, \u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eif he doesn\u0027t take them, then no one else will\u003c/link\u003e.\n\nThe glow of a violet light coming from deeper within the cave. Calming, warming... beckoning. Welcoming him deeper and deeper, promising safety. Some would say that what sounds too good to be true usually is. He would say, \u003clink=\"textWavy\"\u003eFaust was a wise man\u003c/link\u003e.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_DESC":  "Dash foward, spinning and slicing repeatedly for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e120% damage\u003c/style\u003e per hit. The number of hits scales with attack speed.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_25_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players deal 75% damage.",
                    "SS2_LAMP_BODY_NAME":  "Follower",
                    "SS2_NEMHUNTRESS2_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Huntress engages against enemies slowly but ruthlessly with their deadly longbow and double headed hatchet.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Death doesn\u0027t fear itself.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_DETONATE_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eReplaces Special.\u003c/style\u003e. Spit a detonative agent at your \u003cstyle=cHumanObjective\u003efriend\u003c/style\u003e, causing them to explode for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1000-4000% damage\u003c/style\u003e based on how long they were \u003cstyle=cHumanObjective\u003ebefriended\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MOLTENCOIN_LORE":  "Order: Molten Coin\nTracking Number: 446*****\nEstimated Delivery: 09/22/2056\nShipping Method: Standard\nShipping Address: Venetian Police Department, Brithen, Venus\nShipping Details:\n\nHey, I found another piece of evidence relating to that bombing at Parathan Square a couple days ago.\n\nSo, you know how the investigators had to postpone their analysis because the area was way too hot? Well, the space finally cooled off this morning, and I managed to find this melted coin stuck to the pavement. A quick chemical test says it\u0027s probably made mostly of tungsten with a gold coating, and it also hasn\u0027t cooled off since I peeled it off the ground.\n\nI\u0027m not really sure what it could mean, though. Maybe a good luck charm, or a calling card? Either way, I\u0027m sending it to you, since, quite frankly, you need all the help you can get. I mean, 7 people dead, 18 injured, nearly half a million in property damages, and all you\u0027ve got for evidence is a melted coin and a blown-up cafe? Well, you\u0027ve got my sympathy, man. Good luck on the case.\n",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_STICKYOVERLOADER_NAME":  "Overloaded",
                    "SS2_ITEM_CRYPTICSOURCE_DESC":  "Upon ending your sprint, unleash a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eburst of energy\u003c/style\u003e in a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e radius for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e base damage.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NKOTASHERITAGE_NAME":  "Nkota\u0027s Heritage",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_ROOTJUNGLE":  "An outstretched root.",
                    "SS2_MULE_UPHEAVAL_NAME":  "Upheaval",
                    "SS2_NEMHUNTRESS2_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so they left, finding a new home far away.",
                    "SS2_DROIDDRONE_PICKUP":  "Shoots nearby enemies. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eInherits elite type\u003c/style\u003e of the slain elite.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFFORCE_NAME":  "Relic of Force",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_INSECTICIDE_NAME":  "Pest Control",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_GRENADE_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, carry at least 20 Lunar items on Stage 8.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_SPECIAL_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eSlayer.\u003c/style\u003e 1500% scythe dash. heal nearby on kill. hold to increase distance ",
                    "SS2_DRONE_CLONE_COMMAND_DESCRIPTION":  "",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_DESC":  "Upon taking \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003elethal damage\u003c/style\u003e, instead bleed out for \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e100%\u003c/style\u003e of your \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003emaximum health\u003c/style\u003e. Recharges every \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e4\u003c/style\u003e minutes \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(-20% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_CHUNGUS_NAME":  "Chuckling Fungus",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GUARDINGAMULET_DESC":  "Reduce damage taken from behind by \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTBULB_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_MASTERY_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_CYBORG_PRIME":  "\u003ccolor=#42f5b3\u003e\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003ePrimed\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/color\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eHitting \u003ccolor=#42f5b3\u003ePrimed\u003c/color\u003e enemies with a different attack deals an additional \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e300% damage\u003c/style\u003e in an area.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_SCAN_DESCRIPTION":  "Reveal \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eattack vectors\u003c/style\u003e around up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e4\u003c/style\u003e nearby enemies. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eMove into position\u003c/style\u003e to dash forward, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1200% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SPECIAL_SCEPSUBMISSION_NAME":  "Subjunction",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXPURPLE_PICKUP":  "Become an aspect of toxicity.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_FIELDACCELERATOR_DESC":  "As Artificer, kill the Teleporter boss with a Nano-Bomb from 100m away.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_DETONATE_NAME":  "Natural Link",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLASTKNUCKLES_PICKUP":  "Your attacks create explosions at close range.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GUARDINGAMULET_NAME":  "Guarding Amulet",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONELITEKILL_PICKUP":  "Elites drop items.",
                    "SS2_EVENT_SANDSTORM_START":  "\u003csprite name=\"CloudRight\"\u003e\t A sandstorm is approaching...",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_BLAZEBORNE":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eBlazeborne\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eBeing near burning enemies gives bonuses. Larger enemies burn hotter. Blazing elite monsters always burn.\nDamage from fire-based attacks is reduced by 25% and grants \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e5% heat\u003c/color\u003e.\nCompletely immune to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eIgnite.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG2_MASTERY_NAME":  "Cyborg: Mastery",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_NAME":  "Relic of Mass",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_LORE":  "???",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXVOID_PICKUP":  "Become a disciple of the Edict.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_CYCLONE_DESC":  "",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERHEAL_NAME":  "ORDER: Invigoration Field",
                    "SS2_RUNSHROOM_BODY_NAME":  "Rushrum",
                    "SS2_PYRO_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Blazeborne",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_MAGNET_PICKUP":  "Pull surrounding pickups towards you.",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_CLOAKINGHEADBAND_NAME":  "Cloaking Headband",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_MASTERY_DESC":  "As Nemesis Mercenary, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_MERCENARY_NEMESISSKIN_DESC":  "As Mercenary, defeat Mercenary\u0027s Vestige.",
                    "SS2_PYRO_UTILITY2_DESC":  "Consume \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003eheat\u003c/color\u003e to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ehover\u003c/style\u003e in the air.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_NEMESIS_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando: Cornered Gunslinger",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_CLONE_NAME":  "Proliferate",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_STRESSPASSIVE_NAME":  "idk what to call half of this stuff or how to present it to the player",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, with absolutely no regrets.",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_CHEST_NAME_FORMAT":  "{0}\u0027s Birthright",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SECONDARY_SHOOT_NAME":  "Single Tap",
                    "SS2_DROIDDRONE_COMMAND_DESCRIPTION":  "",
                    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_COMMAND_DESCRIPTION":  "",
                    "SS2_BORG_DESCRIPTION":  "The Borg is a well-rounded survivor, prepared for any situation.\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e \n\n \u003c ! \u003e Unmaker is instant and very accurate, making it useful against enemies both at close and long ranges. \n\n \u003c ! \u003e Rising Star shines when dealing with several hard to hit enemies, as it can hit several targets in a short amount of time. \n\n \u003c ! \u003e Overheat Redress vacuums up nearby enemies before exploding - it also provides a quick burst of movement in the opposite direction from which it\u0027s fired. \n\n \u003c ! \u003e Recall can be a very handy asset while exploring the map, to backtrack to the teleporter or to an interactable. Teleporting also deals heavy damage to any enemies you appear inside of.\u003c/color\u003e\n\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NEEDLES_PICKUP":  "Chance to expose enemies to guaranteed critical strikes.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_COMMANDO_ALT1":  "Shock",
                    "SS2_PORTAL_VOIDSHOP_CONTEXT":  "Enter Mysterious Portal",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_90_DECREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "-90% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SECONDARY_NAME":  "Personal Backup",
                    "SS2_INTERACTABLE_DROPPOD_NAME":  "Escape Pod",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_SPECIAL_BANNER_UPGRADE_TOOLTIP":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003e\u003ccolor=#fa78f3\u003eEmpowered\u003c/color\u003e\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eAdditionally grants \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eX% barrier\u003c/style\u003e.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_PYRO_PRIMARY_NAME":  "Scorch",
                    "SS2_BORG_SECONDARY_AIMBOT_NAME":  "Rising Star",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_X4_NAME":  "Apex Predator",
                    "SS2_BANDIT_TRANQ_GUN_DESC":  "Fire a tranquilizer dart for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% damage\u003c/style\u003e, \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eslowing down\u003c/style\u003e and eventually \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estunning\u003c/style\u003e enemies. Can hold up 4 darts.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG2_DESC":  "[temp]CyborgUnlockDescription",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_50_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players deal 50% damage.",
                    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_INTERACTABLE_NAME":  "Broken Shock Drone",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_UTILITY_TELEPORTER_DESCRIPTION":  "Deploy a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ewarp point\u003c/style\u003e. Reuse to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eswap\u003c/style\u003e positions with nearby targets.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG2_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Cyborg, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_GOUGE2":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eGouge\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eApplies 200% damage over time. Capable of critical hits and activating item effects.",
                    "SS2_BORG_SPECIAL_TELEPORTB_NAME":  "Recall",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_TASER_NAME":  "Deadly Voltage",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SPECIAL_MAGNETBALL_DESCRIPTION":  "Fire an energetic mass for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e700% damage\u003c/style\u003e. The mass drops shards that explode for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6x175% damage\u003c/style\u003e and \u003ccolor=#42f5b3\u003ePrime\u003c/color\u003e enemies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_INSECTICIDE_PICKUP":  "Poison enemies on hit.",
                    "SS2_DRONE_CLONE_PICKUP":  "Occasionally \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eduplicates\u003c/style\u003e nearby items.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_ARMAGEDDON2_NAME":  "Armageddon +2",
                    "SS2_MULE_OLDPUNCH_NAME":  "Centrifugal Smash",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERRECOVER_NAME":  "ORDER: Total Reset",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so he left, with newfound purpose in every shell.",
                    "SS2_PYRO_SPECIAL_ALT_NAME":  "DM34 \"Exterminator\"",
                    "SS2_EVENT_OVERLOADINGELITE_END":  "The shocking feelings leave as quickly as they came...",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_NAME":  "Pedestal",
                    "SS2_DRONE_CLONE_SKILL_DESCRIPTION":  "Channels on a nearby item. Upon completion, creates a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eduplicate\u003c/style\u003e of the item.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Nemesis Mercenary: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DORMANTFUNGUS_NAME":  "Dormant Fungus",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Combat Visor",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_LORE":  "Hmm? Oh, Youngling! You are back sooner than expected. Have you completed your search?\n\nOh, dear. Youngling, why are you shivering? Has something hurt you?\n\nYou found something that hurt you? Hmm. Peculiar. Do you have it with you, still?\n\n...I see. Let me look at it, then. Come now, and show me what you\u0027ve found.\n\nHmm. A strange thing, this one. A blazing fire, yet cold to the touch. How unnatural, this is. There\u0027s a certain harmony to it, however. As the heat brings warmth and life, the cold tempers it, and keeps it in check. But in that same way, that bitter cold may bring despair and death without the heat to stave it off.\n\n...Oh, but there I go, rambling once more. You need to be taken care of, Youngling. Please, come with me.",
                    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_INTERACTABLE_CONTEXT":  "Repair Shock Drone",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_75_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+75% Damage Dealt",
                    "SS2_ITEM_PORTABLEREACTOR_DESC":  "Gain \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003efull invulnerability\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e100% movement speed\u003c/style\u003e for the first \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}s\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}s per stack)\u003c/style\u003e of a stage.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_IONBURST_DESC":  "As Executioner, become Supercharged.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_NAME":  "Remuneration",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_FOGGYSWAMP":  "On a mighty archway.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_EXECUTING2":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eExecuting\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDamage and proc coefficient are doubled if no more than one enemy is hit. Kills double gained Ion Manipulator stocks.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPEREARTH_NAME":  "His Shining(?) or maybe Radiant(??) Passion",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_BLEEDING":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eBleeding\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDeals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e240% base damage\u003c/style\u003e over 3s. \u003ci\u003eBleeding can stack. \u003c/i\u003e",
                    "SS2_EVENT_BLAZINGELITE_END":  "The sizzling heat dissipates...",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Commando is a wildcard on the battlefield, capable of turning any situation to his favor.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Blade of Cessation is risky but can build up a lot of damage by stacking Gouge.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Distant Gash can be used to safely apply stacks of Gouge to groups of enemies - take advantage of its piercing!\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Proper balance of melee and ranged combat is key, and Tactical Roll grants high armor to help enter and exit battles.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Submission can be utilized as huge burst of damage, whether it be to aid in an escape or get the jump on an unsuspecting target.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SUBTITLE":  "Vengeful Deserter",
                    "SS2_MULE_NET_DESC":  "Launch a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003enet\u003c/style\u003e, holding enemies within \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e12m\u003c/style\u003e of impact in place and preventing them from attacking for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e5\u003c/style\u003e seconds. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eFlying enemies are grounded\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_POISONOUSGLAND_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_BODY_LORE":  "scary D:",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BABYTOYS_LORE":  "Order: Baby\u0027s Toys\r\nTracking Number: 013*****\r\nEstimated Delivery: 06/07/2056\r\nShipping Method:  High Priority\r\nShipping Address: 431, Golden Shore, Earth\r\nShipping Details:\r\n\r\nHey sweetheart! I\u0027m sorry I couldn\u0027t go, but please, please take these for your baby. He\u0027s so little, but one day he could be the next big UES captain, who knows! I really want to see you two as soon as possible, things have been rough over here since I got ill and I don\u0027t want to put your baby in danger. Love you, please, PLEASE take care!\r\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_URANIUMHORSESHOE_NAME":  "Uranium Horseshoe",
                    "SS2_MIMIC_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "The Mimic",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SNAKEEYES_LORE":  "???",
                    "SS2_BANDIT_TRANQ_GUN_NAME":  "Night Time",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SPECIAL_SCEPSUBMISSION_NAME":  "Subjunction",
                    "SS2_NEMHUNTRESS2_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so they vanished, .",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_BOSSATTACK_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando: Zandatsu",
                    "SS2_ITEM_UNIVERSALCHARGER_PICKUP":  "Periodically refresh a skill on activation.",
                    "SS2_MULE_OUTRO_FLAVOR":  "..and so it left, engine sputtering, directive finally fulfilled.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_NKOTASHERITAGE_DESC":  "Receive \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eitems\u003c/style\u003e upon level up. Rarity of items increases with level.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_PUNCH_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Throw a punch in front for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e150% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_LORE":  "\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eWhat is your legacy?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nNothing but petty vengeance.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eWhat is your identity?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nNothing but a name spoken in disgust.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eWhat do you want?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nNothing but a new purpose.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eWhat do you need?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nNothing but the weapons that I trust.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eSo, where will you go?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nWherever you make me go.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eThen, what will you do?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nWhatever you say you need.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eIs that all, then?\u003c/link\u003e\n\nIf you say it so.\n\n\u003clink=\"textShaky\"\u003eThen go there, and die.\u003c/link\u003e\n\n...\n\nAs long as you\u0027re paying me.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ERRATICGADGET_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003e==========================\n======== CallCutter ========\n===== ALPHA 0.1354.1.12 =====\n==========================\n\nCutting into call TdiM3c4fcQQA.34074... done\nAcquiring audio input from Caller A... done\nCaller B........ done\nEncrypting line... done\nEnable live TTS output?\n\u003eY\n\n==========================\nTEXT-TO-SPEECH OUTPUT BELOW\n==========================\n\u003c/style\u003e\nCaller A: Hey, do you still have the gadget?\nCaller B: Yeah, right here, are we still good to go?\nCaller A: Yes, the deal\u0027s still on...\nCaller A: You haven\u0027t told anyone about this, right?\nCaller B: What, you think I\u0027m stupid? Of course not!\nCaller A: Good. Keep it that way.\nCaller B: I will, I will... Say, are you sure this thing\u0027s safe to just, like, send through the system?\nCaller B: This gadget\u0027s some sort of high-end weapon modification, isn\u0027t it?\nCaller A: Don\u0027t sweat it, the gadget\u0027s perfectly safe. UES doesn\u0027t check their packages. I\u0027ve used their mailing system loads before, and I\u0027m still doing just fine.\nCaller B: Eh, if you say so. I\u0027ll send it through, and I\u0027m expecting fifteen-thousand credits within the next twenty-four hours, as planned.\nCaller A: As planned. Good doing business with you.\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003e==========================\n=====CALL DISCONNECTED=====\n==========================\n\nSevering line..... done\nBacking up recording........ done\nSave text output?\n\u003eY\n",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ARMEDBACKPACK_LORE":  "Order: Militarized Backpack Marked For Return\nTracking Number: 823****\nEstimated Delivery: 2/13/2056\nShipping Method: Standard\nShipping Address: 17 Yule Road, Livingrock, Earth\nShipping Details:\n\nMisfired on a hike. Get your lawyers ready.",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_SUBTITLE":  "[temp]CyborgSubtitle",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_EMERGE":  "Emerge",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_NAME":  "Relic of Duality",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LOWQUALITYSPEAKERS_DESC":  "Chance when getting hit to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003estun\u003c/style\u003e enemies and destroy projectiles in a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}m\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}m per stack)\u003c/style\u003e radius. Chance starts at \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e10%\u003c/style\u003e and increases with \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003elow health\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BLOODTESTER_LORE":  "Return: Broken Blood Tester\nTracking Number: 288*****\nEstimated Delivery: 06/17/2056\nShipping Method: Priority\nShipping Address: Dionysus Pharmaceuticals Headquarters, Pluto\nShipping Details:\n\nWe\u0027re going to need this one repaired before it does our company more harm than good. This thing kept giving us the wrong results every time our MED-E used it. Not only does it clog our workflow, we wind up having to pay out of pocket to the patients since we wrongfully diagnose them, and stick them with needles needlessly. And we can\u0027t claim it as the patient being wrong since it\u0027s all immediately backed up to the servers. We can\u0027t keep shelling out this kind of money, or we\u0027ll be bankrupt by next quarter.\n",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERS_DESCRIPTION":  "Deploy 1 of 4 \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eMicrobot Orders\u003c/style\u003e. Using Orders increases \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eStress\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eHold the key\u003c/style\u003e of an Order to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ediscard\u003c/style\u003e it.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFMASS_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eIncrease maximum health\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eReduce acceleration and deceleration\u003c/style\u003e by a factor of \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003e{1}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DETRITIVETREMATODE_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003e$ Transcribing image... done.\n$ Resolving... done.\n$ Outputting text strings... done.\nComplete!\n\n\n\u003c/style\u003eThis is the logbook of D. Furthen, naturalist aboard the UES [Redacted] in conjunction with the ongoing UES Research and Documentation of Outer Life program. This entry was written at Point Sigma, during an expedition to the dense jungles of Cornea III.\n\n---------------------\n\nI have encountered my first sample of outer life on this planet! What a marvel it is, too. The sample resembles an earthen roundworm, but significantly bigger. I have assigned their common name as \u0027Detritive Trematode\u0027, and will describe their properties below.\n\nâ€¢ Roughly two inches in diameter, and varying in size from about four inches to a foot and a half in length. White coloration.\n\nâ€¢ These trematodes were found feasting on a pile of rotting meat in a damp cavern. The meat was of indeterminate origin, but the presence of other, larger animals is exciting nonetheless.\n\nâ€¢ Upon scooping up a clump of the rotting meat, the trematodes quickly reacted to the movement and began wriggling around, before slowly relaxing. The guard positioned with me, Chevry, I think, was disgusted.\n\nâ€¢ Upon touching one with an ungloved hand to feel their texture, one of the trematodes latched onto my palm and began chewing. It was extremely painful, both to have the trematode on my hand, and when Chevry cut the thing off. Despite that, other than a light gash on my palm, I believe I am fine.\n",
                    "SS2_PEDESTAL_DESCRIPTION":  "Allows survivors to swap an item on the Pedestal for one of equal rarity.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RAINBOWROOT_PICKUP":  "A portion of prevented damage is gained as barrier.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_LIGHTBULB_CONSUMED_NAME":  "Broken Lightbulb",
                    "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_CONTEXT_CANCEL":  "Repel Ethereal Energy...?",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_CHIRRWITHER":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eWither\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eHealth decays over time.",
                    "SS2_MULE_PASSIVE_DRONE_NAME":  "Fail-Safe Assistance",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG_MASTERY_NAME":  "Cyborg: Mastery",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_LORE":  "[temp]CyborgLore",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_STRANGECAN_DESC":  "Inflict 6 debuffs at once to a single enemy.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BANEFLASK_PICKUP":  "Attacks apply bane. Each debuff on Baned enemies increases Bane damage.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_MASTERY_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_BEFRIEND_NAME":  "Symbiotic Link",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_SCEPTER_SCAN_DESCRIPTION":  "Reveal \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eattack vectors\u003c/style\u003e around up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e4\u003c/style\u003e nearby enemies. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eMove into position\u003c/style\u003e to dash forward, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1500% damage\u003c/style\u003e.\n\u003ccolor=#d299ff\u003eSCEPTER: Reveal 2 extra attack vectors and deal 1500% damage.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_BORG_SPECIAL_NOTPREON_DESCRIPTION":  "Blast yourself backwards, firing a greater energy bullet that deals up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edamage% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e. Explodes after time, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e%damage damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_SPECIAL_NAME":  "scythe",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_FEAR":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eFear\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eCauses afflicted enemies to stop attacking and flee. Enemies afflicted with fear take 50% more damage and have their movement speed slowed by 30%.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_PICKUP":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eShocks\u003c/style\u003e nearby enemies, interrupting and stunning them.",
                    "SS2_MULE_KEYWORD_CALIBRATING":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eCalibrating\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eCan be canceled with primary, secondary, or jump to perform more powerful \"calibrated\" variants of those actions.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_UTILITY_TRAP_DESCRIPTION":  "Deploy a device that \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003ecaptures\u003c/style\u003e low health enemies, granting \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eextra money\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eelite powers\u003c/style\u003e to nearby allies.",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_REND":  "\u003cstyle=CKeywordName\u003eRending\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eDeals extra damage to Gouged enemies.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he vanished, humanity lost without a trace.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_PRIMAL_BIRTHRIGHT_LORE":  "The symbols on the parchment are foreign to you. You do not understand what they are, but somehow, you understand the meaning they carry. Power. Will. Authority, and a message. \n\n\"The right to rule is earned through strength and wit, and those alone. It cannot be granted by another. It cannot be granted by birth nor blood. Only strength justifies itself.\"\nYou look back down. The flickering lights of the hull cast strange shapes in the shard. Reflected shadows against its glow, coalescing into shapes that coalesce into figures.\n\nTwo shadows stumble aimlessly around in the reflection, against the backdrop of dawn. Short, stubby shadows. A seed falls into one\u0027s hair, and it laughs and plants it back into the soil. A seed falls into another\u0027s hands. It gently pries the thing open, to learn what will grow.\n\nThe shadows lengthen as the sun moves through the sky. Long, imposing shadows against twilight. Positioned perfectly, like an eerie gate to the light.\n\nOne shadow begins to grow faster still, stretching until the whole world is a blanket of darkness. The lone shadow thrashes against its prison, indistinguishable against the sea of blackness, fiercely refusing to fade away.\n\nOne shadow remains in the light. It stands in front of the now rising sun, eclipsing its light. Rays of golden sun wrap around it, forming a coronal halo for the shadow. Standing out starkly against the world around it- blinding, searing, formless. Selfish. It does not move.\n\nYou squint your eyes, and the symbols hold a new meaning.\n\n\"It isn\u0027t fair.\"",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERREDUCE_DESCRIPTION":  "Temporarly decrease the amount of Stress gained from all sources by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e50%\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e10 seconds.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_UTILITY_NAME":  "Phase Blink",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or harder.",
                    "SS2_PEDESTAL_NAME":  "Pedestal",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_EXECUTIONER_SWINGAXE_DESC":  "As Executioner, slay 12 enemies in a single use of Execution.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_SCEPTER_CLONE_DESCRIPTION":  "Summon a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eclone\u003c/style\u003e behind a target that \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003ecopies your abilities\u003c/style\u003e. Recast to dash to it, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e800% damage\u003c/style\u003e.\n\u003ccolor=#d299ff\u003eSCEPTER: Gain an extra dash.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_NAME":  "Vengeful Deserter",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COMPOSITEINJECTOR_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so she vanished, with no one left to keep her company.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_DELUGE3_NAME":  "Deluge +3",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ELITEDAMAGEBONUS_DESC":  "Hitting an elite monster with a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eskill\u003c/style\u003e has a \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e30%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+10% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e chance to \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ereduce your cooldowns\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e0.5\u003c/style\u003e seconds.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_PRIMARY_SWORD_NAME":  "Aeonium Blade",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_90_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players take 10% damage.",
                    "SS2_NEMHUNTRESS2_BODY_NAME":  "Nemesis Huntress",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_NEMCAPEQUIP_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eBurn yourself\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e10% of your max health\u003c/style\u003e to remove \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e25%\u003c/style\u003e of your \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estress\u003c/style\u003e, and temporariliy reduce incoming \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estress gain\u003c/style\u003e by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e50%\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e8\u003c/style\u003e seconds.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_TYPHOON_NAME":  "Typhoon",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_ARMAGEDDON3_NAME":  "Armageddon +3",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Chirr: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_100_INCREASE_NAME_TOKEN":  "+100% Damage Received",
                    "SS2_KEYWORD_TORCHING":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eTorching\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eAt close range, deals 1.5x damage and has a 75% chance to ignite enemies starting at \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e35% heat\u003c/color\u003e. With \u003ccolor=#D78326\u003e70% heat\u003c/color\u003e or more, has an additional 50% chance to ignite enemies at any range.",
                    "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_75_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN":  "Players deal 25% damage.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_DESCRIPTION":  "The Knight is a skilled expert in melee combat, dueling and parrying foes with precise timing and execution.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e parry.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_PYRO_MASTERY_NAME":  "Pyro: Mastery",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERRECOVER_DESCRIPTION":  "Massively decrease your current amount of stress, while also \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003ediscarding all other Orders\u003c/style\u003e. Stress removed is increased per Order lost.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DIARY_CONSUMED_NAME":  "Written Diary",
                    "SS2_SKIN_NEMCOMMANDO_GRANDMASTERY":  "Minuano",
                    "SS2_EVENT_MENDINGELITE_START":  "The planet begins to mend...",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DIARY_NAME":  "Empty Diary",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SHELLPIECE_PICKUP":  "Block lethal damage. Recharges each stage.",
                    "SS2_MULE_CHARGE_NAME":  "Torque Calibration",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CHIRR_BEASTMASTER_DESCRIPTION":  "As Chirr, throw an ally off a cliff, scrap 20 items, then \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003edie\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_BORG_SECONDARY_AIMBOT_DESCRIPTION":  " \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Quickly fire three seeking shots at contenders in front for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e3xDamage% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_BORG_LORE":  "\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eAudio file found under \"Dr. Rayell\u0027s Testimony\". Playing...\u003c/style\u003e\n\n\"Recording started. Begin testing, Dr. Rayell.\"\n\n\"Thank you. After the EOD\u0027s smashing success with biomechanical augmentations, producing some of the finest combat engineers to ever come out of the department, they proceeded further with slightly more... shall we say, experimental designs.\"\n\n\"How so?\"\n\n\"The department began looking into mental augmentation. It was definitely a leap, to be sure. Augmentation was already very cutting edge, but supplementing - or even replacing a damaged brain? It was a tall order. But the heads thought we could do it, so we obliged.\"\n\n\"Hm. What came of your project?\"\n\n\"Once prototyping was complete, we began the human trials. We got all sorts of folks as test subjects, they were vegetative, mentally unstable, broken people. We were told to fix them as best would could.\"\n\n\"And how did that go?\"\n\n\"It was... It was a travesty. Some of them were simply too far gone. There was nothing we could do. Those were the best cases. Worse was when they rejected the replacements. Some died in a swift immune response. The more cognisant ones begged for us to end the headaches they were having. Some of them just started screaming. They\u0027d scream for hours and hours, sometimes for days even. And then they\u0027d stop. They\u0027d literally scream themselves to death.\"\n\n\"That\u0027s, um, a bit unsettling. Is that all?\"\n\n\"There was one. One who made it through the replacement. And it worked wonderfully. We got him in a vegetative state, no hope whatsoever, and we took him from that, and we gave him - maybe not his full life back, but perhaps something resembling it. You have no idea how thankful I was to hear that he was doing well.\"\n\n\"Well, I suppose that\u0027s good to hear. So, what\u0027s happened to him?\"\n\n\"You know? I\u0027m not sure. Other than some behavioral changes, which is to be expected, he was able to return to society rather gracefully. We\u0027ve done check-ups on him every three months to analyze long-term effects, but... Actually? Now that I\u0027m thinking about it, he didn\u0027t show up for it last month. Oh, well. I\u0027m sure he\u0027s doing fine. I\u0027ll have to contact him about that.\"\n\n\"Um, alright, then. Thank you for your time, Dr. Rayell. Your testimony is... Well, it\u0027s certainly something. I hope to hear more about your projects in the future.\"\n\n\"Very well. I hope you find what you\u0027re looking for.\"\n\n\u003cstyle=cMono\u003eEnd of file.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_UNCLAIMED_RARE":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003eIt isn\u0027t fair.\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GREENCHOCOLATE_NAME":  "Green Chocolate",
                    "SS2_SKIN_NEMCOMMANDO_DEFAULT":  "Default",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_DESC":  "WIP DESC",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_NAME":  "Cyborg",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_SPITBOMB_DESCRIPTION":  "Launch a blob of pheromones that \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eslows\u003c/style\u003e and deals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e750% damage\u003c/style\u003e over time, while \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003ehealing\u003c/style\u003e nearby allies.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MAXHPONKILL_NAME":  "MaxHpOnKill",
                    "SS2_ITEM_SHELLPIECE_DESC":  "Upon taking \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003elethal damage\u003c/style\u003e, instead become \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003einvulnerable\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e3\u003c/style\u003e seconds. Recharges each stage.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_BODY_SUBTITLE":  "Endangered Species",
                    "SS2_PYRO_UTILITY2_NAME":  "Liftoff",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_NAME":  "Ion Burst",
                    "SS2_ENGINEER_LASERFOCUS_DESC":  "Release two beams of energy for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e2x150% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Damage \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eincreases\u003c/style\u003e the \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003elonger a target is focused upon\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_SKIN_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_MASTERY":  "Rogue",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ELITEDAMAGEBONUS_PICKUP":  "Reduce the cooldowns of your skills when attacking elite monsters.",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_SPECIAL_SCEPSUBMISSION_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eAgile.\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eRending.\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eCharge up\u003c/style\u003e, then fire a barrage of up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6 blasts of 4x70%.\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eThe number of shots increases with attack speed\u003c/style\u003e. \n\u003ccolor=#d299ff\u003eSCEPTER: Additionally fires up to {0} lasers which deal {2}% damage.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_MULE_SUBTITLE":  "Directive: Survive",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_DROP_NAME":  "Drop",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_NEMCAPEQUIP_PICKUP":  "Reduce the stress of your situation. \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003eSmoking is bad for you!\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_PASSIVE_NAME":  "Weightless Frame",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG2_GRANDMASTERY_NAME":  "Cyborg: Grand Mastery",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_SUPERTYPHOON3_NAME":  "Super Typhoon +3",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_OUTRO_FAILURE":  "..and so he vanished, retired at last.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_DESC":  "Damaging enemies burns them for \u003cstyle=cMono\u003eFIGURE OUT THIS MATH LOL\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+something% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eBeing hit freezes you for some seconds idfk lol figure out when this item is implemented\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_PRIMARY_SWORD_NAME":  "Aeonium Blade",
                    "SS2_ITEM_MAXHPONKILL_LORE":  "???",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ERRATICGADGET_NAME":  "Erratic Gadget",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_ADVERSITY_DESC":  "Every primordial teleporter is ethereal.",
                    "SS2_MULE_SPIN_NAME":  "Torque Calibration",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_ROCKFRUIT_LORE":  "",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_BOSSATTACK_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, kill an enemy with 10 stacks of gouge or more.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_LEASH_DESCRIPTION":  "Tap to bring your ally to you. Hold to \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003esiphon health\u003c/style\u003e from your friend.",
                    "SS2_KNIGHT_SPECIAL_BANNER_DESC":  "Thrust a banner into the ground for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e750% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Nearby allies \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003esmite\u003c/style\u003e enemies with their attacks, reducing their armor and \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003erestoring health\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_MIMIC_BODY_LORE":  "\"Now, I\u0027d like to see this as something of a learning experience, all things considered. Evolutionary biology has a curious place for mimicry, my friend- certain creatures seek not to be threatening or inviting by their own merit, but rather by the means of seeming to be a different thing entirely. Of course, evolution being random means that this isn\u0027t what we\u0027re dealing with-\"\n\n\"Itâ€™s also not what we\u0027re dealing with because-\"\n\n\"No no, let me finish. In this case we have a very fascinating example, don\u0027t we? A machine emulating another machine in such an animated way, as a means to trick us into getting close- why, it\u0027s positively Wicklerian in design, isn\u0027t it? Whoever made this thing really had a heart for it, don\u0027t you think?\"\n\n\"...Dude, it just steals shit. Nothin\u0027 fancy about it.\"\n\n\"Nature really is beautiful, even in a place like this.\"\n\n\"Shut up and letâ€™s keep moving. Ugh, god, why\u0027d I have to get stuck with this guy?\"\n\n-Signal echoes, UES Contact Light",
                    "SS2_EVENT_FOG_END":  "The fog clears...",
                    "SS2_ITEM_COMPOSITEINJECTOR_DESC":  "Gain \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1 \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+1 per stack)\u003c/style\u003e extra equipment slots\u003c/style\u003e. Trigger all of your equipment simultanesouly.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_UTILITY_LEAP_NAME":  "Striking Rush",
                    "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_EXECUTION_SCEPTER_DESC":  "Leap into the air, then slam an ion axe for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1450% damage\u003c/style\u003e. Hitting an isolated target deals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edouble damage\u003c/style\u003e and restores 3 \u003ccolor=#29e5f2\u003eIon Charges\u003c/color\u003e\n\u003ccolor=#d299ff\u003eSCEPTER: Hitting an isolated target also refreshes this skill\u0027s cooldown by 35%.\u003c/color\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HUNTERSSIGIL_NAME":  "Hunter\u0027s Sigil",
                    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERFIRE_PICKUP":  "Become a harbinger of fire.",
                    "SS2_CYBORG2_PRIMARY_LASTPRISM_DESCRIPTION":  "Charge up a continuous laser that deals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1000% damage\u003c/style\u003e per second, but has \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003edecreased turning speed.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NKOTASHERITAGE_NAME":  "Collector",
                    "SS2_CHIRRHELPER_DESCRIPTION":  "frens with bug :)",
                    "SS2_NEMBANDIT_NAME":  "Nemesis Bandit",
                    "SS2_MULE_OLDPUNCH_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eOverclocking\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. Wind up, and throw a mighty punch forward for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e280% damage\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eDamage is multiplied by charge level, up to 4x\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_CLONE_DASH_DESCRIPTION":  "Dash to your clone, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e800% damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_PORTABLEREACTOR_LORE":  "Eighty seconds. Damned lizards. They\u0027re more cunning than they seemed.\n\nSeventy seconds. She took a moment to breathe. What had once been harsh winds was no still air, contained within the miniature biosphere.\n\nSixty seconds. She counted her bullets.\n\nFifty seconds. Two remaining magazines, a box-worth of shells, one grenade - waterlogged, and a duled knife. Not nearly enough.\n\nForty seconds. She counted their heads.\n\nThirty seconds. The lizards gave her shield a wide berth. Either they were frightened of this new technology, or... they were waiting her out.\n\nTwenty seconds. She loaded her shotgun.\n\nTen seconds. The lizards charged - and she hoped she was ready.",
                    "SS2_TRADER_QUALITY_GOOD":  "\u003cb\u003eGood\u003c/b\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONBOSSKILL_NAME":  "ItemOnBossKill",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Mercenary is a fast-paced, short-range survivor, with the tools to dominate any combat encounter - no matter the odds. \n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Splatter deals devastating damage at close range. Use your other skills to close the distance.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Use Cutthroat to interrupt attacks, or to redirect your dash towards more enemies.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Dispatch is a powerful mobility option in combat, and doesn\u0027t interrupt your reload.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Attack Vectors can be blinked to with no cooldown. This makes Exploit a key skill in navigating intense situations.",
                    "SS2_WARDEN_UTILITY_LEAP_DESC":  "Spin forward and slice in front repeatedly, dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e240% damage\u003c/style\u003e with each slice.",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_NAME":  "Nemesis Commando",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_KEYWORD_STRESS":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eStress\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eGain Stress by being surrounded by enemies, receiving damage, or using Orders. Reduce Stress by dealing Critical Strikes, healing, killing enemies, using certain Orders, and being out of combat.",
                    "SS2_ARTIFACT_HAVOC_NAME":  "Artifact of Havoc",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_UTILITY_DESCRIPTION":  "fear cloud",
