                    "SS2_ITEM_STRANGECAN_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e chance on hit to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eintoxicate\u003c/style\u003e an enemy dealing \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eIntoxicate\u003c/style\u003e stacks up to 10 times. Killing enemies \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003eheals\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{3}\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{4} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003ehealth\u003c/style\u003e per stack of \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eintoxicate\u003c/style\u003e.",
