                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_ORDERSTRIKESHOCK_NAME":  "ORDER: Strike KOPPA",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_BEFRIEND_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION":  "Spit neurotoxin that deals \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e240% damage per second\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cHumanObjective\u003ebefriends\u003c/style\u003e under 50% health. Friends \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003einherit items\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003ewither over time\u003c/style\u003e. \n\u003ccolor=#d299ff\u003eSCEPTER: Your friend follows you between stages, and no longer withers.\u003c/color\u003e",
