                    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_STORM":  "Stormborn {0}",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_PICKUP":  "Every {0} seconds, mark an enemy and strengthen them. If defeated in time, they drop an item; if not, they drop nothing.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SPECIAL_BOSS_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eGouging\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eStunning\u003c/style\u003e. \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eCharge up\u003c/style\u003e, then \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003edash forward\u003c/style\u003e and unleash a devastating series of up to \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6\u003c/style\u003e slashes for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e360% damage\u003c/style\u003e per slash.",
                    "SS2_NEMESIS_HUNTRESS_PASSIVE_DESC":  "Highlight \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eWeak Points\u003c/style\u003e while in combat, which can be struck with all arrows for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e1.5x damage\u003c/style\u003e.",
