                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_INSECTICIDE_DESC":  "As REX, kill an Elite Beetle Queen.",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BLASTKNUCKLES_DESC":  "As Loader, kill a teleporter boss in a single punch.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_ITEMONBOSSKILL_LORE":  "???",
                    "SS2_AMBUSH_MESSAGE_SINGLE":  "\u003cstyle=cShrine\u003e{0} has been ambushed by {1}s\u003c/color\u003e.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FORK_NAME":  "Fork",
                    "SS2_ITEM_BABYTOYS_NAME":  "Baby\u0027s Toys",
                    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_NAME":  "Augury",
                    "SS2_ITEM_HUNTERSSIGIL_DESC":  "After \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003estanding still\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e1\u003c/style\u003e second, create a zone that grants \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{1} \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2} per stack)\u003c/style\u003e armor\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{3}% \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{4}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/style\u003e increased damage to all allies within \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0}m\u003c/style\u003e. The zone lasts until you leave it.",
                    "SS2_BORG_SPECIAL_NOTPREON_NAME":  "Overheat Redress",
                    "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFTERMINATION_LORE":  "Youngling! Ah, I am so excited to see you return! Have you found anything new?\n\nOh? You have! Do show me, little one. There\u0027s no need to be shy.\n\nHm... What have you found this time? It\u0027s sturdy and hollow, but when you shake it... it sloshes, like an overripe nutapple. What a strange shape we have here...\n\nOh? Oh my. You were chased by a monster, you say... It did not follow you here, correct?\n\n...It did not. But of course, it would be hard to find us here, wouldn\u0027t it, Youngling?\n\nHere, I will take this away. Somewhere where it can bring no monsters to us.\n\n...I understand. It is okay to be afraid sometimes, but you cannot let it overwhelm you. Would it not be cruel to another wanderer to find this shape, and suffer dearly for it?\n\nWe will be safe here, Youngling. Come with me. You must be hungry after being out for so long.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_DELUGE1_NAME":  "Deluge +1",
                    "SS2_ITEM_STRANGECAN_LORE":  "Two figures sit, one shivering among a sea of rubble in a frozen burrow. The only lights given are the small remains of a fire, and old sparking wires. Barely any protection against the biting cold.\n\n\"Hey...\" He looks up, distantly hopeful. \"Do you think we\u0027ll ever make it off this rock?\"\n\n\"Hard to say.\" She takes a bite of a ration she found.\n\n\"Well there has to be something we\u0027ve overlooked, right? Some method we just haven\u0027t thought of yet?\" He stands up, and begins pacing around anxiously.\n\n\"Could be.\" Another bite.\n\n\"Maybe there\u0027s some wreckage with working parts we just haven\u0027t found yet, or a problem in the current ones we could fix?\" A shine returning to his eyes, getting himself more hopeful and excited.\n\n\"Definitely possible.\" Another bite.\n\nHe stops as a disgusted look crosses his face. \"Ugh, could you please help me think of something instead of just eating?\"\n\n\"I wouldn\u0027t worry about it.\" Another bite.\n\nHis disgust quickly gives way to blatant frustration and anger. \"Why not?! Don\u0027t you want to get out of here?!\"\n\nShe sighs, and runs a hand through her hair. \"Well sure. But that doesn\u0027t mean we\u0027ve gotta stress over every little thing. We\u0027re alive, ain\u0027t we? We\u0027re lucky we have that much.\"\n\n\"Well... I suppose you\u0027re right... It\u0027d be bad to get worked up right now...\" His expression relaxes as he looks back to the ground.\n\n\"See? Just sit down, relax, and let my old stash warm you up.\" Another bite, as she passes the can.\n",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BLOODTESTER_NAME":  "Medic!",
                    "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_GRANDMASTERY_DESC":  "As Nemesis Commando, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon.",
                    "SS2_CHIRR_HEAL_DESCRIPTION":  "Heal yourself and nearby allies for \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{0}% of their total health\u003c/style\u003e and \u003cstyle=cIsHealing\u003e{1}% more over time\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_NAME":  "Nemesis Captain",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_ARMAGEDDON1_NAME":  "Armageddon +1",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DETRITIVETREMATODE_DESC":  "Enemies under \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{0}% \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{1}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e health\u003c/style\u003e are \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003einfested\u003c/style\u003e for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e{2}%\u003c/style\u003e base damage \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{2}% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e per second.",
                    "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_DESC":  "For each \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003edebuff\u003c/style\u003e on an enemy, gain a \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e3%\u003cstyle=cStack\u003e (+1% per stack)\u003c/style\u003e\u003c/style\u003e chance to fire a void shard for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400%\u003c/style\u003e TOTAL damage.",
                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_PRIMARY_BLADE_NAME":  "Blade of Cessation"
